-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('15', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>1、</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在简书网，有很多假装勤奋好学的青年。他们喜欢寻找捷径，那些干货类的文章，深受他们喜欢。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>捷径是没有的。即使有捷径，也轮不到你们走，早被比你们更有资源更有才气的人抢走了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有些人非常自信自己的天赋和努力，以为进了王佩老师办的写作班就可以提高写作能力。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你得先想清楚一个问题：王佩成为剧作家，他的写作能力是哪里来的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>王佩高中时代就是个文艺青年，那时他读书就远超同龄人。王佩在成为自由职业者之前，就在多家媒体做过，北漂的时候就是北京饭桌圈子里有名气的作者人，到杭州没多久，就是《杭州日报》的主笔。他写过无数专栏，创办过《新西湖》。早在博客早期，他就创办独立博客《白板报》。他是牛博网的上半身写手。他跟马云一起办过杂志。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>王佩每天熬夜读书。他随身带小红本，背诵很多唐诗宋词。他也大段大段地背诵莎士比亚剧本的台词。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大多数人一辈子读书的数量，不如王佩在3年时间内读过的书多。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大多人凭一辈子的努力，也做不到杭州日报的高级编辑。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大多数人一辈子的努力，也做不出《新西湖》这个档次的杂志。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当你跟王佩学写作，你觉得他那一套对你管用么。或者姚明教你打篮球，你以为你就能成为篮球高手么。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>再想想王佩的那种写作方式对你有没有用。他是剧作家，也擅长写散文。如果你是一个写哲学思辨文章的，或一个写科技文献的，你马上会明白王佩认为的好汉语，在你的领域根本不适用。在你的领域适用的汉语，王佩却不会欣赏。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>也有人想跟刘淼老师学写作。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>刘淼老师天生聪明，而且有文艺天赋。他是中国比特币的早期人物，他是个人博客网站的先驱，他是街头摄影家的组织者，早在多年前就办过一个叫《在街头》的摄影团体，最近刚刚自杀的任航就是其中的会员。他虽然是复旦经济学科班出身，艺术方面的知识远超大多数文科生，涉猎的文学作品流派种类也超越普通文科生。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大多数人的文艺感受力不如刘淼，如果办一个摄影团体，会让摄影家嗤之以鼻。普通人不会有判断艺术作品好坏的能力，不知道怎样的作品才是好作品。这种评判能力，多半是天生的。正如有些人在互联网时代，还只能欣赏一些肤浅的流行音乐。不是她找不到更好的音乐，不是互联网上没有资源，而是以她的品位，只欣赏那些低端的音乐。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们的文字感有王佩和刘淼那么强么？如果没有，别指望自己可以成为优秀的写作者。天赋，真的是天生的，没有就是没有，60%的天赋，从你还是个受精卵时代就确定了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>2、</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>真正好学的人，不会到简书寻找干货。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>随便一套大学教材，知识的密度和可信度都超过简书首页文章百倍。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>没有经过一个领域系统学习和深入的人，是不可能懂得知识的结构体系的。你们没有能力架构自己的知识体系，只能到简书和知乎之类的地方寻找片言只语的“干货”，这些干货只是一堆无法组建成蛋白质的氨基酸，因为你们没有RNA做模板。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我看到很多人在我的文章下评论，质问我这样写有什么意义。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我只能告诉你：我写作是为了在江湖立一个名号，是为了多认识一些门当户对的同类，不是为了给你们送干货的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>真正的干货，在那些干巴巴的大学课本里，在那些专业手册里，在学术专著里。你们不读那些书，却到简书找干货，是大脑出问题了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>即使是中学课本，也是干活满满。真正学懂中学物理化学的人，在所有的大学毕业生里不到10%。大多数聪明勤奋的留学海龟，也未必明白用5伏12安培60瓦的充电器给苹果手机充电是否安全。很多挣钱挣到一个亿的发烧友，也搞不懂功放和喇叭的阻抗匹配。虽然这些都是中学物理的内容。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在简书找到的干货，不会比欧姆定理更干。在简书找到的作者，不会比鲁迅更好。在简书找到的思想家，不会比马克思休谟更伟大。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>即使是学校逼你学的中国革命史，马克思主义哲学，毛泽东思想，邓小平理论，也是干货满满。你不知道那是干货，因为你肤浅无知。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>见识是天生的。正如很多运动天赋和音乐天赋都是天生的。没有一个真正的音乐家是可以完全靠后天训练出来的。见识和品味的极限，不是你今天努力的程度，而是你的基因和从小形成的人格。没有这种见识的，给他大城市，给他互联网，给他一堆伟人，他却狗咬吕洞宾。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>伟大的思想摆在你面前，你只会破口大骂，或者质问作者那是什么意思。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们寻找的干货，不过是一块马蹄铁，你们关心如何让自己更好地做牛做马讨主人的欢心。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一个二十多岁的人，不去好好钻研一门学问，学一门技艺，不去把中学课本和大学课本学懂，不去涉猎伟大的思想，却到简书寻找捷径，这是丢了高铁飞机，去找马蹄铁。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>3、</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们不必羡慕别人的成功。别人的天赋比你好得多。不仅大脑聪明是天赋，天生勤奋也是天赋。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们不要指望自己通过努力就能成功，那是骗你的。大多数人应该做的，是认清楚自己的平庸，甘心做一个平庸的人。以平庸人的生活态度要求自己。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们也许读过很多励志故事，比如某人本来懒惰，忽然努力起来，就突飞猛进。别指望了，能够忽然变得努力，是一种天赋。有这种天赋的人凤毛麟角，无论是凤毛还是麟角，都未必轮到你。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你要知道，当你沉迷于简书网的首页文章里找干货，本身就是一个标志：你是一个平庸的人。你不喜欢深度思考学习训练。你只希望走捷径。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>简书的创始人很会思考。简书的编辑也很会思考。他们把很多鸡汤文章推到首页，因为他们知道会思考的人很少，而大多数人不会思考。而投资人感兴趣的，是你在多大程度上吸引了大多数用户。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>承认自己笨，承认自己没有勤奋的天赋，承认自己没有努力上进的天赋，正如承认自己的身体缺陷一样，不是可耻的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一些本无天赋的人，或者看了励志文章后变得很努力，但是这种努力不会让你变得更有天赋，只能为你抢到机会。比如一个平庸的人占据了一个本该适合天才的职位。这不是社会的进步，而是社会的悲剧和人类的损失。也是你自己的损失，因为你只有活得地位的成功的快感，未必有做事的快感。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一个典型的例子是那些四平八稳的学术论文。他们打造各种范式，制定各种门槛规范，炮制各种套路，最后出来的是光鲜亮丽的套在垃圾思想上的严谨包装。为什么99%的学术论文都是垃圾？因为99%的研究者都是平庸的人通过努力获得了本该给天才占据的职业。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>4、</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>不要假装你们勤奋好学。你们并不勤奋，也不好学。最勤奋好学的人，比如我，很害怕进入书店或图书馆，那里的知识浩瀚如海，让人觉得自己无比渺小，即使能活一千年，也不足以汲取知识之万一。像我这么勤奋好学的人，经常为了搞懂一个小问题打开几百个网页，所以需要极大的电脑内存。我读书少，是因为我太好学，唯恐一个新领域引起我的兴趣就耗尽我的体力和生命。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>因为我勤奋好学，大部分时间都浪费在学习、思考、迷惘、痛苦、厌世，留给做别的事情的时间很少，所以我很难做成大事业。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>勤奋好学略低一点的人，比如刘淼和王佩，他们泡在书海里，读大量的精品书，认识大量的精品人。他们涉猎面还是太广，所以一生没有大成就。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>勤奋好学程度更差的人，对太多的人类知识并无兴趣，只专攻自己的某个本行，在极小的领域深挖进去，成为一代学霸，学者，教授，博士，学术泰斗。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>比这类学霸更不好学的人，只认真学习自己工作中用到的东西，成为行业专长人物，他们是优秀的工人，农民，技师，医生，华尔街投资人，马云，王健林，比尔盖茨。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但是你们不同。你们不属于我们中间的任何一个档次。你们没有鉴赏力，你们无论花多少时间，无论多么努力刻苦，你们不是在垃圾中寻找精品，而是在精品中搜寻垃圾。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你们的一生，就是把各种垃圾当干货，背着沉重的干货包袱前行。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>精品放在你们面前，你们只会破口大骂，或者觉得作者不知所云。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我嘲笑的是你们，不去好好学点有用的知识，却到鸡汤和干货里找捷径。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>耶稣说：不要把珍珠放在猪面前。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>更不要把珍珠放在狗面前，它只吃粪，还咬不让他吃粪的人。</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('16', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>很多人都认可比喻是最重要的修辞方法，很多人会说比喻有什么难的，取两个相似的东西类比就行了。刘勰在《文心雕龙》说:“比之为义，取类不常：或喻于声，或视于貌，或拟于心，或譬于事。”哲学家黑格尔谈比喻时说:“为着避免平凡,尽量在貌似不伦不类的事物中找出相关连的特征，从而把相隔很远的东西出人意外地结合在一起”。朱自清先生更是提出过“远取譬”的思想，就是用不是很像的东西进行类比，用陌生的东西进行类比，比喻越新奇，效果就越出彩。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>能在寻找陌生意象方面有出类拔萃之功效的作家中，有三位大师是公认的绝顶高手：张爱玲，钱钟书，村上春树。舒明月老师就很喜欢张爱玲和钱钟书，认为他们的比喻能力是种基因突变。村上的比喻：“我喜欢你就像喜欢春天的熊”一亮相就惊为天人。那他们的比喻到底好在哪里呢？<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><h3 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'><strong>一.张爱玲：远距离比喻的大师</strong></h3><p><img src=\"C:\\pl\\2297654-e758b3a8b07d1478.jpg\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>张爱玲能够用许多远距离的比喻。在这些比喻中，相去甚远的本体和喻体的组配,蕴含了作者的匠心独运和巧钞搭配的机智、造成了一种新鲜的陌生化的比喻修辞效果、撞击着人们思维的惯性与惰性。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">1.地板正中躺着一双绣花鞋，微带八字式，一只前些，一只后些，像有一个不敢现形的鬼怯怯地向他走过来,央求着。(《江玫瑰与白玫瑰》)</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>鬼而鞋子，鞋子而鬼。我第一次看到这个比喻，惊叹还能用鬼来比喻鞋子，但是结合上下文语境，又觉得非常合适，突出了房间的幽秘和人物的神秘。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.南美洲的曲子，如火如茶，是灿烂的春天的吵嚷声。(《谈音乐》)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>以春天的吵嚷声喻曲子，是说出了那曲子的什么呢?好呢?还是不好？但不管好与不好，你听到这句话却不愿意就当耳旁风，你已经被吸引了。因为你根本不道春天的吵嚷是什么，但你却也好似知道它是什么。或许好与不好本身就是狭隘的。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">3.日光像个黄蜂在头上转，营营扰扰的，竟使人痒刺刺地除出了汗。《中国的日夜》</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>触觉，听觉，视觉一下子全都联系了起来，张爱玲似乎总能将感觉全都打通，给人身临其境的“3D”描写。</p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'><strong>二.钱钟书：用抽象比喻具体，用具体比喻抽象的大师</strong></h4><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2297654-bbda39621b59b1b0.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><br style=\'color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>钱钟书先生用比喻之妙就多体现在他对传统比喻模式的突破,转变语境来拟寓事物、事理。比如说，他就常常借用一些抽象无形的事物去比喻具体可感的事物。同样的，他也常常借用一些具体可感的事物去比喻抽象无形的事物，比如感觉等。且看下面例子：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">1.褚哲学家害谗疹地看着苏小姐,大眼睛仿佛哲学家谢林的`绝对观念’。——《围城》</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“绝对观念“是哲学的一个概念，简单说就是指绝对精神中的最后的和最高的概念”，也就是最崇高的范畴。用这种最高范畴比喻哲学家的目光，体现了苏小姐在哲学家心中的崇高地位。作者借用他们形式上的相合把两种看似风马牛不相及的事物联系在一起,使语言活泼幽默。把哲学家面对女色时贪婪的目光描写得形象逼真。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">2.写方鸿渐的妻子：身材将来准会跟她老太爷那洋行的资本一样雄厚”。</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>身材的高大、肥胖是可视可感的,而洋行的资本却是无形的难以估量的,作者用资木的雄厚比身材的发展,以模糊性的事物比具体的事物,给人留下想象、回味的余地。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">3.她眼睛并不顶大，可是灵活温柔，反衬得许多女人的大眼睛只像政治家讲的大话，大而无当</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>用政治家的大话比喻许多女人空洞的大眼睛，形象传神，又带着浓浓的诙谐滋味。令人不觉拍手称妙。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">4.“把方鸿渐忘了算了，可是心理忘不了他，好比牙齿嵌去了，齿腔空着痛，更好比花盆里种的小树，要连根拔它，这花盆就得碰碎。”</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>两个比喻，用拔牙和拔树根把人物欲望不能的痛苦的抽象心理表现得具体可感。想忘吧，如拔牙的疼痛刺激着没法忘；不想忘吧，如拔树盆碎的心抓着揪着忘不了。</p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'><strong>三.村上春树：本体和喻体差异极大，却和谐统一的大师</strong></h4><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2297654-a7810ed07bee04d3.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“村上式比喻”的特点主要表现在三个方面：第一，本体与喻体间的相异度极大，形成巨大的落差；第二，本体与喻体间多为隐性相似性，实际上是一种超感官的相似性；第三，喻体往往是不常见的、生疏的、抽象的、深奥的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>看几个例子：<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊新月之夜如瞎眼的海豚一般悄然而至。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊海驴这种动物，总的说来颇像早些年的中国人。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊袋鼠爸爸以才华枯竭的作曲家般的神情定定地看着食料箱里的绿叶。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊后脑麻酥酥的，就像帽檐朝后扣了一顶小号棒球帽。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊计程表起跳时的“咔嚓”声如火药枪筒射出的散弹一样直捅我的脑门。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">＊所谓人生便是这么个东西，好如植物种子被不期而至的风吹走，我们在偶然的大地上彷徨。</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>是不是感觉很奇妙，村上属于那种能有奇特的比喻绝对不随便比喻的作家。他最有名的的比喻是《挪威的森林》中下面这段话：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">你有多么喜欢我？”绿问。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“全世界森林的老虎都溶化成黄油那么喜欢。”我说。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“特喜欢你吔，绿。”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“有多么喜欢？”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“春天的熊那般喜欢呀。”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“春天的熊？”绿又仰起脸。“那是什么呀，春天的熊？”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“你一个人走在春天的原野上，对面来了一只毛像天鹅绒的眼睛圆圆的可爱的小熊，这么对你说啦，说：你好，小姐，和我一起打滚吧。然后你和小熊抱在一块儿，在长满三叶草的斜坡上骨碌碌打滚，玩了一整天。不错吧？”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“真不错。”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">“就这么喜欢你。”</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>初看这段比喻，什么老虎融化成奶油啦，和春天的熊在草地上打滚啊，你觉得莫名其妙，可是又有一种难以言说的贴切感。细细想来，村上绝对是运用同感的大师，“我喜欢你，像喜欢春天的熊”就是牢牢把握了恋爱那种“毛茸茸”的可爱感觉，并在寻觅表述这种感觉时，准确找到了“春天的熊”这个意象。运用这个方法，你还可以这么写“我喜欢你，像喜欢融化冬雪的第一缕阳光。”怎么样，比直接写“我对你的爱像阳光”这种老套的比喻要好很多吧？</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2297654-4655d1572dfd92ef.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>综上所述，写出好的比喻不仅需要天赋，更需要后天大量的练习。舒明月老师在《善用比喻是一种基因突变》种告诫我们：“不是要刻奇地模仿，穿个棉布裙、披个长直发去树顶上一脸淡然地破坏绿化，而是要功利地学她，目光灼灼地看她是怎么做到的。艺术修为是个系统工程，大家勉力吧！”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>写出好比喻是写出好文章的重要一步，不积跬步无以至千里。我们一起向大师们学习，多多写出令人惊艳的比喻吧！</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('17', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2582273-31eb94e6cbe7cf26.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">图片发自简书App</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>﻿“我们都是张三李四一样的平凡人，一夜暴富、一夜暴瘦或者一夜爆红这样的小概率事件，和我们相距甚远。我们能做的，不过是在机遇来临前，做好自己该做的一切，准备好应该有的一切。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>1</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我是我们大学里文学社的副社长，除了负责社团日常的琐事，也分管社团的微信公众号，所以大二上学期我主动关注了很多微信公众号，学习它们的运行。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有天睡觉前，读到了一篇文章，作者是文长长。惊讶于她能把日常的琐碎描写得深入浅出，有思考但不过分矫情，通篇读下来，便留意了作者的信息。看到“简书”两个，便在手机上搜索了一下，后来下载了软件，开始了真正意义上的写作。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我接触文学非常晚，高一才知道郭敬明、韩寒是谁。高三才读余华、毕飞宇、史铁生、刘振宇等严肃文学作家的作品。高三那年，莫言获得了诺贝尔文学奖，班里有几个学生开始摒弃玄幻小说，捧着莫言的《蛙》热火朝天地读，同时警惕班主任锐利的目光。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我当时特别高兴，终于有人和我一样喜欢读这类书了，终于可以和同学讨论书里的人物和故事情节了，没想到，他们读莫言的《蛙》是为了在语文作文中写上一两句书中的话，为了给自己的作文贴金，这无可厚非，但心里的那片火瞬间熄灭。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>第一次拿起笔写小说，是在我高一某天的晚自修，印象非常深刻：故事描写了一个生活在农村的哑巴的一天。小孩子向他扔石头；大人嘲笑他；哪怕是去小餐馆吃面条，碗里的面也比别人少。哑巴只有一个朋友，是村里一个智商有点不正常的小女孩。文章最后的情形是哑巴牵着小女孩的手，背着夕阳的余晖回到哑巴的住处。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>故事的很多细节现在已经遗忘，不过写了半个笔记本那么厚，现在觉得真是不可思议。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我把这个故事拿给坐在我前边的好友看，她没有任何评价，只告诉我看罢哭了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>高中学业紧张，见缝插针般的书写，倾诉欲无穷无尽。每天都期待着晚自修——就着一沓试卷，一行一句的表达，不知道为什么写，也不知道写的是什么。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>午休的时候，舍友都睡觉，我躬着身子读七堇年。从《被窝是青春的坟墓》到《尘曲》，忘了休息，还嫌时间不够用。年华从我左手蜿蜒到故事里的新疆。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>《被窝是青春的坟墓》里的第一篇文章叫《远镇》，是篇关于成长、失去与得到的小说。是我至今最喜欢的短篇小说，没有之一。于是我索性便以“远镇”为笔名。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>2</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大一的时候，模模糊糊地觉得自己应该写点什么，于是三天打鱼两天晒网的看书，书写。散散漫漫，散文歪打正着发在杂志上，还挺开心。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大二的暑假开始用简书，才明确自己对于书写这件事原来是这般的爱。其实我真正意义上的创作，就是从接触简书才开始的，因为这之后我才有源源不断的灵感和动力，以及完整的作品。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>也许这个年纪，语言避免不了不假思索的煽情，但写起东西来会觉得整个世界都是自己的。可以悲情，可以胸襟辽阔，可以大吐为快。那种感觉，妙不可言。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>话说回来，其实我对于写作这件事，并没有太多的规划，有了灵感便写，写出来反反复复地修改。完成后就找平台发表。后来竟陆续收到杂志的邀请，公号的邀请，小说入围了全国的比赛等，这都是“意外之财”。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>欣喜之余，更多的是担忧。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>因为我知道自己还差很多很多，于是我有意识地开始补习。积累四字成语、俗语。从中文系学姐那儿淘来《中国现当代文学三十年》、《小说家的是三堂课》等书。其实都是为了自己的作品能够更加“文学性”。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>后来有幸作为作者参加一期杂志的交流会，是一家60年代创刊的市级杂志，办公室主任的编辑面对许多像我这样年轻的作者分享自己的心得，在提问环节，我颤巍巍地举手，说了自己的疑惑：总感觉非中文专业的人写作少了点什么。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>编辑老师笑了，他说中文系是最不出作家的专业，很多人都笑。最后编辑老师把头偏过来，看着我：<strong>写作无非是多读，多思考，多写。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我把“多读，多思考，多写”写在笔记本上。在以后的生活过程中，这句无比朴素的话的分量，越来越重。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>3</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>今天早晨，照例打开手机，点开简书，没想到自己不知不觉已经写了十万字。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这十万字里，有一半是严肃类、青春类的小说作品。也有对生活、对大学、对亲情感悟的散文。看着那些作品，想起很多个漫长的下午一个人泡图书馆看书，想灵感，写作的情形。有时候看到精彩处，即便有同学约我出去玩，我也会拒绝。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实在我成长过程中，我丢失了很多能够维持我一生的兴趣。所以才导致现在的我紧紧地握着“写作”，生怕哪天失去它，从此一无所有。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我从小就非常喜欢画画，高中的时候如果不是发生了一系列非常不愉快的事情，现在的我很可能就是那个背着画板，手指上沾满颜料的美术专业的学生。那是一段非常灰色的时月，每次想起来都会难过。我看到有人写“一切痛苦都会过去”，我觉得是放屁，这段回忆我会记一辈子。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>高中的美术老师后来遗憾地对我说，可惜了，真的，我当美术老师这么多年，第一次因为一个学生不学美术而可惜。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>即便对成长过程中的所失耿耿于怀，时间也拖着我们走了很远的路。我试图重新摸索那年丢失的、对生活的热望，于是，余华《活着》里的富贵救了我，小说救赎了我。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这一路少不了迷惑与自我怀疑，何况敏感如我。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>写了十万字，有小说、散文、随笔等类型，题材有现实讽刺、成长的感悟、爱情友情亲情、励志、大学生活等，很杂很多，所以我现在不知道自己擅长写什么，适合写什么，对于以后的写作方向也非常的模糊，只知道自己非常钟爱严肃文学作品。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>也不知道自己写作为了什么，只是心里时常冒出一些东西，脑子里偶尔就钻出一面脸，如果不用键盘打出来，会憋得难受。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有时候会觉得自己写的小说没有充分表达出最初的想法，需要啰嗦，情节混乱。有时候又觉得散文情感不够，力度不够，语言太直白，言不达意。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有时候予以很高期望的作品上不了首页，被杂志拒绝。特别严重地怀疑自己的写作能力。别人都写的那么好，才华横溢，信手拈来，觉得自己永远都达不到。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有时候告诉自己：可能你并不适合当个作者。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有时候，很长时间写不出来一个字。很艰难写就的文章，不满意，一怒之下删除，重写，在删除，再重写。往复几次，自己精疲力尽，心情烦闷。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>还好啊，自我痊愈的能力磨砺了出来。安慰一句“少年啊，长路漫漫。”也就重新收拾自己的心情，下笔，表达，斟酌。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大学这一年半，我总是告诉自己要认真生活，不必合群也不要刻意的冷漠，没有人可以说话就用大把大把的时间看书填充生活，有人可以讲，便诚恳地、一五一十地挥霍青春。但生活里放不下的，就是电脑的桌面上那个没有写完的小说文档。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>也许这条路上很多的疑惑，如今还没有一个明确的答案。也许这一切的疑问，在我写完二十万字后、在下一个作品完成后，就会自然而言懂得。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我才22，无所畏惧！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>希望以后，在我再次迷茫、不知所措、怀疑自己的时候，我自己能看看这篇文章。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>最后送给大家我非常喜欢的一句话，也自勉：</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>多些努力，少些期待，你想要的终究会来。</strong></p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('18', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>公园里的梅花开了，孤傲绝艳！</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>昨天饭后散步，去了学校对面，高新运动公园。腊梅开得正盛，一团团棉花般，顶在枝头，寂寞地绽放着。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一簇一簇，躲在光秃秃的杂木林中。腊梅与枯草颜色一致，没有叶子，一根根枝条插在地上，若不是香气吸引，很容易被游者忽略。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-80ccecd9aa075a63?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-80ccecd9aa075a63?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>腊梅多年前就见过，小时侯院子边种有。深冬时节，春节前后，不经意间一阵清香扑鼻。<strong>我见过的腊梅，都是白色的，在棕色枝条上，不张扬，不夺目。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>以前的冬天会下雪，腊梅却不怕冷。天气转凉，腊梅笔直地挺立，雪落下，给梅花盖了一层被子。本以为，花朵早被严寒吓得脱落，几天后转晴，雪化了，枝头还是白的。走近一看，吓了一跳，腊梅竟然比雪前更精神。每一片小花瓣，都露出洁白的牙齿，看着我，似乎在笑。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>父亲常常指着腊梅告诉我，看看花都不怕冷，你就成天守着火炉，还不快去写作业！每每这时，我就躲进里屋，翻开课本写道：墙角数枝梅，凌寒独自开！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>我不是在赞扬梅花，只是听着寒风把窗子吹得瑟瑟发抖，总觉得自己，就是一枝可怜的梅。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong><b style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\"></b></strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-a50c889adc6bbbb0?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-a50c889adc6bbbb0?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>多年以后，当我第一眼见到腊梅，心底深处是同情的。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>时令刚过“雨水”，寒早已消退。走近看，腊梅也快开罢了。春天尚未发芽，我倒庆幸梅花的凋谢。与寒风搏斗了一个冬，想必梅花早就“精疲力竭”。稍作休息，又要吐芽抽枝。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>优秀的物种，无论是动植物，还是高级的生命，从来不会因季节转换，而停止成长。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong><b style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\"></b></strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-0d13fbd171ef17ef?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-0d13fbd171ef17ef?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>梅在我心中，是普通植被，难以比拟的。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>近距离地观察腊梅，还发现一个有趣的细节。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>腊梅或是经历了寒冬的锻造，枝条异常柔软。好事者把腊梅枝，当绳子一样，挽个结；或是把两个枝条绑一起。腊梅可不怕折腾，只要根连着，花开不败。有根腊梅枝上，我看到拇指大的凸起小锤，估计就是多年前“结巴”留下的疤痕。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>梅可真不易，自然的挑战，人类的戕害。正是愈挫愈强吧！腊梅易活，花繁，花香浓，花期延续着人们最难熬的时节。</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-38f23d314a9a1f62?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-38f23d314a9a1f62?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>在兴安公园，今天见到了另一种梅，红花。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>红梅和腊梅，简直就是找不到一点雷同的姐妹。红梅枝高大，类似于桃树，花朵像桃花，只是花瓣、花蕊，都要多几倍。我拉下一根枝条，细细数到底有多少片花瓣，数来数去没个定值，便作罢。大约也有十五六片，紧紧地簇拥着，或许也是为了相互依靠取暖吧！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>借助百科得知，腊梅属蜡梅科，红梅归李科，不知从植物界如何圈定，总之谱系差别大。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>相同的是，他们选择了同一个季节绽放，且在“与世无争”的深冬。真不容易，像梅花一样，选择孤独，傲立霜雪，需要多大勇气啊！</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong><b style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\"></b></strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-dc960e9159ee4a44?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-dc960e9159ee4a44?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>前一天赏腊梅，天色灰暗未留念。红梅的花朵，娇艳欲滴，怎么能按耐得住呢！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>二月将尽，多数植被尚在冬眠，梅灿烂地绽放，显然是报春的。我和妻子，用各种角度，留住梅最绚烂的笑脸，记录季节的结束和开始。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>拍着拍着，我意识到，与平常所见的花朵照片，迥然不同。花有相似，景却各异。红梅的背景，要么是枯黑的枝条，要么是荒野的干草。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>红花也需绿叶衬？寒梅何需绿叶衬！</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong><b style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\"></b></strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-7c86aa62ef629d6c?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-7c86aa62ef629d6c?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>或者说，整个萧条的冬季，不都是梅的衬托吗？</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>和谐的搭配是一种艳，刚烈的对比是另一种美。</strong>论刚烈、论孤傲，谁可与梅相匹敌呢！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>如此看来，不难理解，梅为何列“梅兰竹菊四君子”之首。当之无愧啊！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>告别几树红梅，转身之际，又留下一个有趣的镜头。一堵古香古色的围墙，红梅的枝头，正从墙顶伸出。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>暮色已沉，墙头的红色花朵显得模糊，仍不失“红杏出墙”的意境。<strong>从深冬娇艳到早春，孤傲的梅从不缺少典故。</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-203ba0a9e0edc05a?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3719418-203ba0a9e0edc05a?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>要走出公园时，路边的花坛里，几株矮矮的树丛貌似也开花了。走近一看，是海棠。<strong>海棠四季常青，零散的几片叶子中间，几个深红的花骨朵，像是害羞的姑娘，或许是闻到了，春天的气息吧！</strong></p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('19', '\n				\n	<blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">阅读是件快乐的小事，但领略它的美好，相信它的意义，我们的生命一定会在潜移默化之中升华。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p></blockquote><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-fd16650a2c5f5abe?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-fd16650a2c5f5abe?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>国产综艺的口碑风向，眼看要变。从早期选歌手、撕名牌，到如今最强大脑、诗词大会、念信和朗诵刮起“清新”之风，其实也不过几年时间。不是说选秀和跑男不好，但综艺“清流”的出现，至少拓展了好看的新维度。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>近来最受热议的，是央视新推的节目《朗读者》。目前，这档综艺已经在豆瓣上达到9.2的高分。要知道，在挑剔的豆瓣网友眼里，《奇葩大会》也才8.3分。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>之前凭借诗词大会圈粉无数的董卿，是《朗读者》的制作兼主持。节目形式很简单，邀请“朗读者”选择散文、歌词、致辞、书信等文本，讲述选择这个文本的理由以及自身的故事，最后通过朗读的形式呈现给观众。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-567eeba1f6842ca2?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-567eeba1f6842ca2?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>每期《朗读者》会设定一个串联全场的主题词，第一期是“遇见”。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>踢踢印象最深的是许渊冲先生的段落。其实读书的时候，听老师讲学林掌故，就有不少关于许渊冲先生：（蜜汁）自信、多情、善感。是表扬，但好像总有点弦外之音。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但《朗读者》请到许渊冲先生，桥段安排得很精彩。落座之前，许先生递给董卿一张名片，写着“书销中外百余本，诗译英法唯一人”。这是惊堂木一拍，提醒诸位，好戏要开场。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>然后，96岁的老先生开始谈笑风生，接引到人生第一首译诗，林徽因的《别丢掉》。许先生讲这首诗的创作背景，是林徽因得知徐志摩的死讯，故地重游，写“一样是明月，一样是隔山灯火，满天的星，只有人不见，梦似的挂起”。说着说着，许先生自己红了眼眶。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-0773aac31d8c15d4?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-0773aac31d8c15d4?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-0f211f8f6afe1ea4?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-0f211f8f6afe1ea4?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>原来，之所以要译这首诗，是想送给50年前喜欢的一个女同学。镜头对准坐在台下的太太，许先生照说不误，女同学当时有喜欢的人，后来也失去了联系，直到50年后，因为许先生荣获大奖，报刊登载，才重新联系上。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>白云苍狗，半世浮华，各自有了家庭的归宿，再回首，许先生说：“生活的每一天都能欣赏，有时候失败有失败的美。”才子多情，命运幽深，都在里头了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>让一个成名已久的翻译家来讲述跨越50年的情感故事，时而轻快时而深沉，张弛之间，就抓住了观众。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-092da8b9d7760115?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-092da8b9d7760115?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>濮存昕出场的时候，董卿抛了一个问题：“生命中有没有这么一个人，可以这么说，没有他就没有濮存昕？”。濮存昕讲述了儿时的经历。那会儿他腿脚有病，绰号“濮瘸子”，受到欺凌和压迫，难掩自卑。直到荣国威大夫医好他，让他过上正常人的生活。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当花白胡子的濮存昕拿出老舍先生平易亲和却隽永温存的散文《宗月大师》，表达对荣大夫的感恩，观众会收到一种暗示：名人和我们一样，有难言的苦衷，有铭感的恩情。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>柳传志是知名企业家，观众必定好奇，他会朗读些什么。结果他不念诗词歌赋，不聊管理智慧，选了自己在儿子婚礼上的致辞。其中还有非常世情的幽默感。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-135d3b7811bd7a79?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-135d3b7811bd7a79?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>看到曾经那么远的商界传奇，诉说和常人一样的情感，自然缩短了与观众的距离。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>名人和我们一样有血有肉，有喜有悲，那就极尽展现，这是《朗读者》的聪明之处。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>制作者深切地知道，故事和话题从反差里来。名流离观众远，就拉近一点。而普通人和观众相差无几，那就强调特殊性。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>蒋励是一名妇产科医生，曾经作为无国界医生成员去到阿富汗，为战地的孕妇接生。在几个月的时间里，她先后接生了数千个婴儿。在生命转瞬即逝的地方，迎接了如此之多的新生命，这是常人难有的体验。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>因而，蒋励朗读Bob Dylan的Blowing in the wind，赋予了这首流行经典全新的意义。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-38fe6357f5774ff6?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-38fe6357f5774ff6?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当时刻置身生命流转的蒋励念出“一个人要仰望多少次，才能看见天空，一个人要有多少只耳朵，才能听见人们的悲泣”，我们也会有不同的触动。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>周小林和殷洁是一对普通夫妻。因为对妻子的承诺，周小林倾其所有，用十年时间，为妻子打造了一个开满鲜花的山谷。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-66a9c4f5c6d03782?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-66a9c4f5c6d03782?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>结婚26年来，他们不时写一些情话，为彼此读情诗也是生活常态。当他们一起朗读“最会写情话的人”朱生豪写的情书，“醒来觉得甚是爱你”，成了过往佳话的现实寄托，感动着我们这样营营役役辛苦打拼的人。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>老文本加上新故事，就有了与众不同的意义。这是《朗读者》成功的秘密。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但是，聊了这么多心理上的暗示，踢踢还是要说，《朗读者》的风靡，主要还是得益于这届观众越来越行。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-2588088b2caac118?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-2588088b2caac118?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当董卿站在舞台中央，她交代了《朗读者》的来龙去脉：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">我当了21年主持人，而今仿佛回到了起点。《朗读者》中的朗读二字重文字，者字重人。我们要展现有血有肉的真实人物情感，并感动于他们让我们遇见了大千世界。我对于一档有着人文精神的电视节目的追求，终于要实现了。</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>呼应这段话的，是对阅读的反复强调。她在片头里提醒：<strong>“</strong>多长时间没有阅读了，很久了吧，大家都觉得那是学生时代的事情，或者说它只属于一小部分人，朗读属于每一个人。”她还说：“我们每天都面对着很大的压力，天天想着赶紧工作，赶紧忙完手里的事，赶紧看看收入，所以应该有这么一个契机，让大家能够安静下来去看一档节目。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>朗读时的表达，朗读者的故事，把人与文字绑定在一起，这种相遇，其实就是“阅读”。除了摆脱疏于学习、知识匮乏的焦虑，我们为什么要坚持阅读？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>踢踢以前写过：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">消极点说，读书是对现实生活种种平庸与逼仄的逃避。透过书籍构筑起的独立的心灵世界，每一位读者都能够领略人类的智性之光和性情之美，对前人或同时代高人的世界观也有所了然。这种纯粹的参照和成长是很多事情无法给与的。而且，读书给人以更大的自由，在书籍构筑的世界里，很少有阻碍，因为想象是不会碰壁的。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">积极来看，读书是对现实的补偿。生活中难有的、难以实现的梦想，书里可以教你实现。现实里的无力感，书里可以营造情境，让你不觉代入，进而兴观群怨，浑然忘机。这种体验也许是无用的，但也因为无用，所得的快乐才更纯粹。哪怕终要回到现实，也不再会因为一时一刻的阻滞而灰心丧气。</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>看来，同意这种说法的人越来越多。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-e0c3dfefc2631f3f?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-e0c3dfefc2631f3f?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-45108a503cf43a83?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-45108a503cf43a83?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-626377c27eb2523a?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-626377c27eb2523a?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>《朗读者》只是基于阅读的感性精选，但因为形式恰当，分寸合宜，真真正正地展现出阅读的魅力：有理，有情，有既定的故事，更有延展的空间。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有网友说，《朗读者》最打动人的，是帮助观众找回了“初心”。所谓初心，引用“毒舌电影”推送里的一句话就是：“读书，是门槛最低的高贵之举。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>《朗读者》之类的节目得到日益频繁的讨论，本身也意味着阅读之必要，情感之诉求，正在取代空泛无聊的恶搞，填补大量碎片时间。哪怕喜爱阅读的出发点是“若有诗书藏在心，岁月从不败美人”，至少，已经有更多人走在正确的道路上。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这一点，踢踢想由衷地为你们鼓掌。阅读是件快乐的小事，但领略它的美好，相信它的意义，我们的生命一定会在潜移默化之中升华。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-fa04d4844e833648?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/326721-fa04d4844e833648?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>关注踢踢的人，离幸福更近一点</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('20', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>初三毕业那年，我考了不错的成绩，被我们县城的高中录取，父亲很是高兴，因为我们祖祖辈辈，连一个高中生都没有。可是，想到接下来三年的学费和生活费，父亲又愁白了本来就不多的黑发。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>看看家中，已经没有可以卖的东西了。养了好几年的羊，在我将要上初中的时候卖了。家里只有两三亩地，父亲身体不好，所以每年收成都不好，粮食不够吃，总是借完东家借西家。奶奶是个盲人，每天需要人照顾，每天也要吃药，父亲偶尔捡捡破烂，但是，能卖多少钱呢？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当时，很多邻居劝我父亲：“女娃子识个字就行了，别读书了，你看你家都穷成这样了，赶紧出去打工才是正道。”对于这样的论调，父亲听到一个怼一个：“孩子有那个本事，我砸锅卖铁也得供，不能让她长大后埋怨我。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>可是，说是这么说，就算砸锅卖铁，我家也凑不够一千多的学费啊！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当时的我已经16岁了，别的孩子正值叛逆期，可是我没有，因为我知道，我没有叛逆的资格。但是那次，我却偷偷地留了一张纸条，坐上了去郑州的大巴，准备利用暑假打工赚学费。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>开往郑州的大巴，破烂而炎热，发出令人作呕的汽油味，我怀着忐忑不安的心情，踏上了未知的路程。身上一共带了10块钱，已经作为车费给了大巴司机，所以我已经身无分文。我曾经考虑过没钱了怎么办，于是就从家里偷偷带了五个馒头，决定找到工作之前就啃馒头，只要饿不死就行。我盲目乐观地相信，我一定能够找到工作。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>我清楚地记得，当时的我穿了一件很旧很旧的牛仔裤，是邻居给的，屁股上已经破了一个洞，我打了个补丁，格外显眼。上身穿白绿色T恤，其实是绿色的，但洗得发白了。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>我上高中之前，一件新衣服都没有穿过，所有的衣服不是别人给的，就是在路上捡死人穿过的衣服。</strong><em>（我们这里，人死了以后就把他所有穿过的衣服扔掉，于是爸爸总带我去捡。）</em></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>到了郑州的时候，已经晚上9点多了。我下了车，四处一片辉煌，来来往往的行人不断，四处都有三轮车在叫客：“到哪里去啊，坐车不坐？”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不敢和任何人讲话，因为我听说外面的世界有很多骗子，所以我像个沉默的傻子一样，谁跟我讲话我都是摇头，然后又一边为郑州的繁华而惊异。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>当时怕吗？那是当然，从一个小乡村来到完全陌生而又繁华的省会，年龄又那么小，还是一个女孩子。可是，我这个人就这么一个脾气，即使再害怕，也会要紧牙撑下去，假装自己很勇敢。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我直奔进了长途汽车站的厕所，喝了很多凉水，感觉自己清醒了很多，然后找了一个角落，啃着已经发凉的干馒头，大口大口地吃起来。周围很多背着行李席地而坐的人，所以没有人在意一个小女孩的窘迫。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>等到第二天，天色发亮的时候，我就从冰冷的地上醒来了。这一夜我睡得很不安稳，中间醒了很多次，迷迷糊糊地又睡过去。那个时候的郑州，还没有麦当劳、肯德基什么的，也有一些人在车站过夜，所以我并不十分害怕。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我拍了拍衣服，腿已经发麻，过了很久才缓过来。于是我抱着剩下的馒头，开始找工作。只要是贴着“招工”的字眼，我都会进去，可是，没有一家收兼职人员，尤其是我这么小的年龄，尽管我谎报为18岁，但是当时我又瘦又小，因为吃不饱饭而发育不良，看起来更不像18岁了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>被拒绝了一次又一次，我走在郑州的大街上，很多街道的名字我都忘记了，也可能当时并不留心去记，只记得几个字“东建材”，因为当时不懂是什么意思，所以记忆很清楚。我还清晰地记得，当时过马路，馒头袋子忽然烂了，馒头滚了一地，当时我感觉全世界的眼光都集中在我的身上，我狼狈地跑去捡掉落的馒头。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>太阳炙烤着大地，柏油路走起来的时候很烫脚，整个街道都懒洋洋的，有的店家挥挥手就赶走了我，有的同情我给我一碗水喝，还有的要给我十块钱，我拒绝了。我想凭借自己的本事做兼职，我不是要饭的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>找了一天，天色都暗了下来，我不知道自己走到了哪里，总之我走到了一个很不起眼的街道，来到了一家私人饭馆。老板听了我的遭遇后，就留了我下来，干一个半月，给300。我高兴极了，当天晚上，我和老板的女儿住在了一起，她睡床，我打地铺，除了一条破席子，什么都没有，但是我很感激，很欢喜。从那之后，我便开始了自己的打工生涯。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>每天早上五点，我要起床打扫饭店，大概有10个包厢和一个大厅，我要全部擦一遍，把地拖了，然后就开始择菜洗菜，我最讨厌的就是剥姜皮，用指甲扣，火辣辣的，很疼。店里除了老板和老板娘以及老板女儿，只有我一个服务员。而老板娘和老板女儿是不干活的，老板只负责做菜，所以其余的任务，全都落在了我的身上。我要洗菜端菜，还要收盘子洗碗，直到夜里12点才休息，而中间，所有人都去午睡的时候，我旁边都会堆了很多很多的盘碗，一遍一遍的清洗。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>来吃饭的人，并不总是老实的，有的会出言调戏我，有的会在我收盘子的时候故意看我的胸口，当时觉得很恶心，我又没发育好，穿得又严严实实的，有什么可看的？还有的会说：“跟我走吧，我带你吃香的喝辣的，保管你不用这么辛苦。”饭店的生意很火爆，这样的话每天都有人说，每次我都沉默不语，就当自己没听见。还好，没有人对我大发脾气，也没有人对我动手动脚，所以，我还可以忍下去。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>只是，到了晚上很困很困的时候，总是想哭，太累了，真的太累了，一天16个小时，我连十分钟的休息时间都没有，我真的好累啊。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>老板的女儿性格不算太好，总是让我给她洗衣服什么的，袜子内衣都是我来洗，把我当成佣人一样对待，一天晚上，当我说我好累我想休息的时候，她拿了一把剪刀对着我：“信不信我一剪刀扎死你也没人知道！”我当时害怕极了，但还是倔强地不说话。她又忽然咯咯地笑了：“看你吓得，逗你玩呢，你给我乖一点，我不会杀了你的。”那个时候我觉得，外面的世界，真可怕啊，我真的很害怕。她的性格阴晴不定，有的时候也会温柔地跟我说几句话，说说她那个优秀的男朋友。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>最严重的是有一次我收拾客人喝完的酒瓶，用一个筐子装起来摆在后院，摆放的时候，没注意有一个底部烂了一般的瓶子，手掌按上去，一下子血流如注，滴滴答答地落在地上，我强忍着继续干活，最后血实在止不住，才跑到一边的诊所包扎了一下，医生让我不要碰水，可是，洗碗如何不碰水呢？于是我一边带着伤口一边干活洗碗，直到现在，我手掌里还有一道疤痕，就是那时候留下来的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>夜里的时候不知道哭过多少次，但好在终于熬过来了，一个半月后，老板如期给了我300块钱，我踏上了回去的大巴，在父亲东借西凑之后，终于凑齐了学费。交学费的时候，很多一毛、两毛、五毛、一块的零钱，厚厚的一沓，是父亲平时在吃饭都吃不上的情况下，一点一点从嘴里抠出来的。很多学生和老师在第一天就传开了：“咱们学校重点班，来了一个捡破烂老人的孙女”。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>可是，那是我爸爸，不是我爷爷。</p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">后记：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">人生就是一段体验，富人体验享乐生活，穷人体验艰辛生活，各种体验的结合，就构成了一段人生。对于过去的苦难，现在我已经不觉得辛苦，也没有怨天尤人，我只是想，无论是什么样的出身，什么样的生活，只要未来是充满希望的，就可以坚持下去。而现在，文字就是我的救赎，是我的疗愈之道。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">愿你也能早日找到疗愈自己的方法。</p></blockquote>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('21', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">入职安居客三年从工程师到Team Leader，见证了Android团队一路走来的发展历程。因此有心将这些记录下来与大家分享，也算是对自己三年来一部分工作的总结。希望对大家有所帮助，更希望能得到大家宝贵的建议。</p><h2 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>一、三网合并</h2><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>三年前入职时安居客在业务上刚完成了三网合并（新房、二手房、好租和商业地产多个平台多个网站合成现在的anjuke.com，这在公司的历史上称之为三网合并）,因此app端也将原先的新房、二手房、好租和商业地产多个app合并成为了现在的安居客app。所谓的合并也差不多就是将多个项目的代码拷贝到了一起组成了新的Anjuke Project。下面这张图能更加直观的呈现当时的状况。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-7f3d0d069e520ff4.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-7f3d0d069e520ff4.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这一时期代码结构混乱、层次不清，各业务技术方案不统一，冗余代码充斥项目的各个角落；甚至连基本的包结构也是胡乱不堪，项目架构更是无从谈起。大家只不过是不停地往上堆砌代码添加新功能罢了。于是我进入公司的第一件事就是向Leader申请梳理了整个项目的结构。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>而后随着项目的迭代，我们不断引入了Retrofit、UniversalImageLoader、OKHttp、ButterKnife等一系列成熟的开源库，同时我们也开发了自己的UI组件库UIComponent、基础工具库CommonUtils、基于第三方地图封装的MapSDK、即时聊天模块ChatLibrary等等。这之后安居客项目架构大致演变成了由基础组件层、业务组件层和业务层组成的三层架构。如下图：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-12a602cdba1361fc.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-12a602cdba1361fc.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其中业务层是一种非标准的MVC架构，Activity和Fragment承担了View和Controller的职责：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-952b113dda3fee39.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-952b113dda3fee39.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>前面这种分层的架构本身是没太大问题的，即使到了现在我们的业务项目也已然是基于这种分层的架构来构建的，只不过在不断的迭代中我们做了些许调整（分层架构后面在介绍组件化和模块化的时候会详细介绍）。但是随着业务的不断迭代,我们慢慢发现业务层这种非标准的MVC架构带来了种种影响团队开发效率的问题：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Activity和Fragment越来越多的同时承担了Controller和View的职责，导致他们变得及其臃肿且难以维护；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">由于Controller和View的揉合，导致单元测试起来很困难；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">回调嵌套太多，面对负责业务时的代码逻辑不清晰，难以理解且不利于后期维护；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">各层次模块之间职责不清晰等等</li></ul><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">鉴于三网合并时期我还未加入安居客，所以对这一块的理解难免有偏差，如果有安居客的老同事发现文章中的描述有不对的地方还望批评指正。</p></blockquote><h2 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>二、由RxJava驱动的MVP架构</h2><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一种技术架构无法满足所有的业务项目，更不可能有一种架构方案能够一劳永逸。正如上一节中提到的随着业务的不断迭代，现有架构的缺陷逐渐浮出水面，项目架构必需不断升级迭代才能更好地服务于业务。</p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>2.1 MVP的设计与实现</h4><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在研究了Google推出的基于MVP架构的demo后，我们发现MVP架构能解决现在所面临过的很多问题，于是我们学习并引入到了我们的项目中来，并针对性的做了部分调整。下图呈现的是安居客MVP方案：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-aa6fa3673ca8b9aa.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-aa6fa3673ca8b9aa.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>以前面提到的三层架构的方案来看是这样的：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-0000fadf4026d686.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-0000fadf4026d686.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">基于此架构我在GitHub上开源了一个项目<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/BaronZ88/MinimalistWeather\" target=\"_blank\">MinimalistWeather</a>，有兴趣的小伙伴可以去clone下来看看，如果觉得对你有帮助就给个star吧。 :)</p></blockquote><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">View Layer</strong>: 只负责UI的绘制呈现，包含Fragment和一些自定义的UI组件，View层需要实现ViewInterface接口。Activity在项目中不再负责View的职责，仅仅是一个全局的控制者，负责创建View和Presenter的实例；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">Model Layer</strong>: 负责检索、存储、操作数据，包括来自网络、数据库、磁盘文件和SharedPreferences的数据；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">Presenter Layer</strong>: 作为View Layer和Module Layer的之间的纽带，它从model层中获取数据，然后调用View的接口去控制View；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">Contract</strong>: 我们参照Google的demo加入契约类Contract来统一管理View和Presenter的接口，使得某一功能模块的接口能更加直观的呈现出来，这样做是有利于后期维护的。</li></ul><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>另外这套MVP架构还为我们带来了一个额外的好处：<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">我们有了足够明确的开发规范和标准</strong>。细致到了每一个类应该放到哪个包下，哪个类具体应该负责什么职责等等。这对于我们的Code Review、接手他人的功能模块等都提供了极大的便利。前面提到的<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/BaronZ88/MinimalistWeather\" target=\"_blank\">MinimalistWeather</a>就是为了定规范定标准而开发的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这一时期我们还在项目中引入了RxJava，很好的解决了前面提到的嵌套回调的问题，同时能够帮助我们简化复杂业务场景下的代码逻辑（当然RxJava的好处远远不止这么一点，对RxJava不了解的同学可以去翻翻我之前<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20687178?refer=baron\" target=\"_blank\">一系列关于RxJava的文章</a>）。我们也将网络库升级到了Retrofit2+OKHttp3，它们和RxJava之间能更好的配合。</p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>2.2 MVP带来的新问题及解决方案</h4><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>是不是升级到了MVP架构就高枕无忧了呢？很明显不是这样！MVP架构也会带来以下新的问题：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">由于大量的业务逻辑处理转移到了Presenter层，在一些复杂的业务场景中Presenter同样会变得臃肿难懂。细心的同学可能注意到了前面的架构图中的Model层有个Data Repository模块，Data Repository在这里有两个作用：一是可以将原本由Presenter处理的部分逻辑转移到这里来处理，包括数据的校验、部分单纯只与数据相关的逻辑等等，向Presenter屏蔽数据处理细节，比如作为Presenter就不必关心Model层传递过来的数据到底是来至网络还是来至数据库还是来至本地文件等等；二是我们引入了RxJava，但是只有网络层中的Retrofit能返回Observable对象，其他模块都是返回的还是一些非Observable的Java对象，为了能在整个Presenter层中都体验RxJava带来的美妙之处，因此可以通过Data Repository做一层转换；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">现在的MVP架构中最重的部分就是Model Layer了，这一点从前面的架构图中就能体现。因此这就要求我们在Model层的设计过程中职责划分要足够清晰，分包更明确，耦合度更低。至于分包大家可以参考<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/BaronZ88/MinimalistWeather\" target=\"_blank\">MinimalistWeather</a>的方案：db包为数据库模块、http包为网络模块、preference包是对SharedPreferences的一些封装、repository包就是前面提到的Data Repository模块；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">同时还有一点需要注意，很多人在使用RxJava的过程中往往忘记了对生命周期的管理，这很容易造成内存泄露。<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/BaronZ88/MinimalistWeather\" target=\"_blank\">MinimalistWeather</a>中采用了CompositeSubscription来管理，你也可以使用RxLifecycle这类开源库来管理生命周期。</li></ul><h2 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>三、组件化与模块化</h2><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>去年下半年我们Android团队内部成立了技术小组，基础组件的开发是技术小组很重要的一部分工作，所以组件化是我们正在做的事；模块化更多的是现有的方案受到来自业务上的挑战以及受到了Oasis Feng在MDCC上的分享和整个大环境的启发，现在正处于设计规划和demo开发的阶段。</p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>3.1 组件化</h4><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>组件化不是个新概念，通俗的讲组件化就是基于可重用的目的，将一个大的软件系统拆分成一个个独立组件。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>组件化的带来的好处不言而喻：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">避免重复造轮子，节省开发维护成本；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">降低项目复杂性，提升开发效率；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">多个团队公用同一个组件，在一定层度上确保了技术方案的统一性。</li></ul><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>现在的安居客有是三个业务团队：安居客用户app、经纪人app、集客家app。为了避免各个业务团队重复造轮子，团队中也需要有一定的技术沉淀，因此组件化是必须的。从本篇的第一节大家就能看到组件化的影子，只不过在这之前我们做的并不好。现在我们需要提供更多的、职能单一、性能更优的组件供业务团队使用。根据业务相关性，我们将这些组件分为：基础组件和业务组件。后面在介绍模块化的时候会有进一步的描述。</p><h4 style=\'margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.7; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\'>3.2 模块化</h4><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>自从Oasis Feng在去年的MDCC2016上分享了模块化的经验后，模块化在Android社区越来越多的被提起。我们自然也不落俗的去做了一些研究和探索。安居客现在面临很多问题：例如全量编译时间太长（我这台13款的MacBook Pro打一次包得花十多分钟）；例如新房、二手房、租房等等模块间耦合严重，不利于多团队并行开发测试；另外在17年初公司重新将租房app捡起推广，单独让人来开发维护一个三年前的项目并不划算，所以我们希望能直接从现在的安居客用户端中拆分出租房模块作为一个单独的app发布上线。这样看来模块化似乎是一个不错的选择。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所以我们做模块化的目的大致是这样的：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">业务模块间解耦</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">单个业务模块单独编译打包，加快编译速度</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">多团队间并行开发、测试</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">解决好租App需要单独维护的问题，降低研发成本</li></ul><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">15年Trinea还在安居客的时候开发了一套插件化框架，但受限于当时的团队规模并且插件化对整个项目的改造太大，因此在安居客团队中插件化并未实施下来。而模块化其实是个很好的过渡方案，将项目按照模块拆分后各业务模块间解耦的问题不存在了，后续如有必要，再进行插件化改造只不过是水到渠成的事。</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>来看看安居客用户app的模块化设计图：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-8fa2a7065f0bfe19.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-8fa2a7065f0bfe19.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>整个项目分为三层，从下往上分别是：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Basic Component Layer: 基础组件层，顾名思义就是一些基础组件，包含了各种开源库以及和业务无关的各种自研工具库；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Business Component Layer: 业务组件层，这一层的所有组件都是业务相关的，例如上图中的支付组件AnjukePay、数据模拟组件DataSimulator等等；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Business Module Layer: 业务module层，在Android Studio中每块业务对应一个单独的module。例如安居客用户app我们就可以拆分成新房module、二手房module、IM module等等，每个单独的Business Module都必须准遵守前面提到的MVP架构。</li></ul><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>同时针对模块化我们也需要定义一些自己的游戏规则:</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">对于Business Module Layer，各业务模块之间的通讯跳转采用路由框架Router来实现（可能会采用成熟的开源库，也可能会选择重复造轮子）;</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">对于Business Component Layer，单一业务组件只能对应某一项具体的业务，对于有个性化需求的对外部提供接口让调用方定制;</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">合理控制各组件和各业务模块的拆分粒度，太小的公有模块不足以构成单独组件或者模块的，我们先放到类似于CommonBusuness的组件中，在后期不断的重构迭代中视情况进行进一步的拆分（这一点的灵感来源于<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.jianshu.com/p/www.trinea.cn\" target=\"_blank\">Trinea</a>的文章）;</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">上层的公有的业务或者功能模块可以逐步下放到下层，合理把握好度就好；</li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">各Layer间严禁反向依赖，横向依赖关系由各业务Leader和技术小组商讨决定。</li></ul><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>对于模块化项目，每个单独的business module都可以单独编译成APK。在开发阶段需要单独打包编译，项目发布的时候又需要它作为项目的一个module来整体编译打包。简单的说就是开发时是application，发布时是library。因此需要你在business module的gradle配置文件中加入如下代码：</p><pre class=\"hljs groovy\" style=\'background: rgb(246, 246, 246); margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 15px; border-radius: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: none; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4285; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \"Courier New\", monospace; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: pre; -ms-word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-size-adjust: none;\'><code class=\"groovy\" style=\'padding: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \"Courier New\", monospace; font-size: 12px; white-space: pre; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\'><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"color: rgb(133, 153, 0); box-sizing: border-box;\">if</span>(isBuildModule.toBoolean()){\n    apply <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"color: rgb(42, 161, 152); box-sizing: border-box;\">plugin:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"color: rgb(42, 161, 152); box-sizing: border-box;\">\'com.android.application\'</span>\n}<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"color: rgb(133, 153, 0); box-sizing: border-box;\">else</span>{\n    apply <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"color: rgb(42, 161, 152); box-sizing: border-box;\">plugin:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"color: rgb(42, 161, 152); box-sizing: border-box;\">\'com.android.library\'</span>\n}</code></pre><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>如果我们需要把租房模块打包成一个单独的租房app，像下面这样就好：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-37ad790d45334f32.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-37ad790d45334f32.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我们可以把Basic Component Layer和Business Component Layer放在一起看做是Anjuke SDK，新的业务或者项目只需要依赖Anjuke SDK就好（这一点同样是受到了<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.jianshu.com/p/www.trinea.cn\" target=\"_blank\">Trinea</a>文章的启发）。甚至我们可以做得更极致一些，开发一套自己的组件管理平台，业务方可以根据自己的需求选择自己需要的组件，定制业务专属的Anjuke SDK。业务端和Anjuke SDK的关系如下图所示：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-94b4f4b6e547607c.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-94b4f4b6e547607c.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>最后看看安居客模块化的整体设计图：</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-f4a5503a8f792733.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1167421-f4a5503a8f792733.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>模块化拆分对于安居客这种比较大型的商业项目而言，由于历史比较久远很多代码都运行五六年了；各个业务相互交叉耦合严重，所以实施起来还是有很大难度的。过程中难免会有预料不到的坑，这就需要我们对各个业务有较深的理解同时也要足够的耐心和细致。虽然辛苦，但是一旦完成模块化拆分对整个团队及公司业务上的帮助是很大的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>以上是我的简单总结以及对模块化的一些思考，不足之处还望大家批评指正。后面模块化的demo完善后我会把它放到GitHub，并再出一篇文章详细介绍模块化的设计实现细节。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>参考资料：</p><ul style=\'padding: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.csdn.net/article/2015-12-16/2826499-android-app-architecture?locationNum=7&amp;fps=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csdn.net/article/2015-12-16/2826499-android-app-architecture?locationNum=7&amp;fps=1</a></li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.trinea.cn/android/didi-internationalization-android-evolution/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.trinea.cn/android/didi-internationalization-android-evolution/</a></li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.tianmaying.com/tutorial/AndroidMVC\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tianmaying.com/tutorial/AndroidMVC</a></li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.diycode.cc/topics/362\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.diycode.cc/topics/362</a></li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/MDCC2016/Android-Session-Slides/blob/master/02-From.Containerization.To.Modularity.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/MDCC2016/Android-Session-Slides/blob/master/02-From.Containerization.To.Modularity.pdf</a></li></ul><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">如果你喜欢我的文章，就关注下我的知乎专栏或者在GitHub上添个star吧！</p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 22px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">知乎专栏：<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/baron\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/baron</a></li><li style=\"line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\">GitHub：<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://github.com/BaronZ88\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/BaronZ88</a></li></ul></blockquote>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('22', '\n				\n	<blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">陶潜东篱采菊花，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">黄巢怒披黄金甲。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">重阳把酒寓长寿，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">人生宜减不宜加。</strong></p></blockquote><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-c953b381cce79358.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-c953b381cce79358.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">冯桂林菊瓣壶</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊瓣壶</strong>是是模仿为盛开的菊花创制的一款经典紫砂<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">筋纹器</strong>。筋纹器是紫砂器型当中一类制作<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">难度比较大</strong>的一类器型。特别是像菊瓣壶这样线条繁复的器型，对于制作的工艺要求极高。首先壶的整体要被等平均分成几十瓣，每一瓣之间不能有丝毫差异，否则一望便知。而且壶身、壶盖、壶嘴、壶纽要纹路和谐统一。壶盖要能够<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“通转”</strong>，不管转到哪个方向都可以和壶身纹路保持对应。同时，筋纹器由于纹路繁复，因此对泥料也要求较高，必须选择<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">可塑性较强</strong>的泥料，否则不易成型。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-bd85d5c9570ea440.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-bd85d5c9570ea440.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">另外，除了工艺方面的高要求以外，在整体的艺术美感上也十分重要，比如纹路的粗细条数要和器型相协调，并不是越多越好，还要准确把握纹路之间凹凸的程度，做到<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">凹凸有致</strong>。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">菊瓣壶自明代创制以来，作为一款长盛不衰的器型一直受到人们的青睐，一方面和此壶造型美观有关，另一方面和<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊花</strong>本身拥有的丰富内涵有很大关系。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-2cae6d94d95d8472.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-2cae6d94d95d8472.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">四君子</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">菊花是梅兰竹菊<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“四君子”</strong>之一。菊花一般都生长在比较偏僻的地方，而且花期较其他花都晚，一般在深秋。周敦颐曾说：<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊，花之隐逸者也。</strong>自古以来菊花就象征着凌霜飘逸 ，特立独行，不趋炎势的<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">世外隐士</strong>。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">当年<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">陶渊明</strong>虽然写了《桃花源记》，但毕竟<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“桃之夭夭，灼灼其华”</strong>，桃花太过妖艳轻佻了，他更爱的是可以令人忘虑消愁，怡然自得的菊花。所以他才经常<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“采菊东篱下，悠然见南山”</strong>。而且菊花是在霜降以后才开花的，所以它那种不畏寒霜的顽强生命力也暗合陶渊明<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">不为五斗米折腰</strong>隐居山林自食其力的精神。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-8d595a9d730fb4bb.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-8d595a9d730fb4bb.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">南山菊</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">唐代的<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">元稹</strong>也非常喜欢菊花。他也曾写过一首<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">《菊花》</strong>：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">秋丛绕舍似陶家，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">遍绕篱边日渐斜。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">不是花中偏爱菊，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">此花开尽更无花。</strong></p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>诗中提到他效仿陶渊明在家周边都种满了菊花，可见他是最偏爱菊花的。同时也提到了菊花的另外一个特点，就是菊花盛开的时候是深秋时节，其他花全都凋谢了。而秋天是肃杀的季节，古代处决犯人都选择在<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">秋后问斩</strong>，所以深秋盛开的菊花又透出一股肃杀之气。元稹这里只是用了一句中性的“此花开尽更无花”，因为他毕竟是文人士大夫，人生主要课题无非是忠君事主，就算不得意，也只能写写诗，抱怨两句而已，不会有太多其他想法。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">但是就在元稹写下这句诗之后几十年，出现了一个也喜欢借菊花写诗的人，他就是晚唐农民起义领袖——<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">黄巢</strong>，他也曾是个书生，也梦想考取功名报效朝廷，但是在多次参加科举皆未中之后，愤然写下了一首这<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">《不第后赋菊》</strong>，相当于立下了造反的誓言：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">待到秋来九月八，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">我花开后百花杀。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">冲天香阵透长安，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">满城尽带黄金甲。</strong></p></blockquote><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-f4cbb65c5bfbc8e1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-f4cbb65c5bfbc8e1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">黄巢</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">诗中<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“我花开后百花杀”</strong>虽然意思和元稹那句<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“此花开尽更无花”</strong>一样，但是明显杀气腾腾，后面的<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“满城尽带黄金甲”</strong>更是赤裸裸地表达出了要带兵攻入长安推翻李唐自立为王抱负。黄巢写完这首诗后不久就在老家组织农民起义，当时社会政治黑暗，民不聊生，所以起义军一呼百应，实力迅速壮大。最后黄巢居然带领六十万大军孤军深入，直取长安，把皇帝都赶到四川去了。占领长安后他成功<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">登基称帝</strong>，国号<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">大齐</strong>，建元<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">金统</strong>，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">兑现了他当初的誓言</strong>。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">当然，最后由于各种原因黄巢发动的农民起义还是失败了，自己也身首异处，战死虎狼谷。<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">黄巢人生的宿命正像是菊花的宿命</strong>，虽能在深秋迎霜盛开，但是随之而来的就是寒冬腊月，凋亡在所难免。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-f0f59ed8fa752999.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-f0f59ed8fa752999.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">重阳节</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">那黄巢为什么在诗的第一句非要待到重阳九月八呢？因为菊花一般在农历九月才会盛开，所以古代又把农历九月又称为“菊月”。而在九月九日重阳节更是有赏菊的习俗，唐代诗人孟浩然有诗云：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">待到重阳日，还来就菊花。</strong></p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>因为重阳节那一天菊花开得最灿烂，约上三五好友，一起外出登高赏菊、吟诗作赋，可谓是乐事一件。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当然，重阳节赏菊之人的心情并非都好，宋代著名女词人<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">李清照</strong>在一年的重阳节赏菊的时候心情就些<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">伤感</strong>，于是便写下了一首<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">《醉花阴》</strong>：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">东篱把酒黄昏后，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">有暗香盈袖。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">莫道不消魂，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">帘卷西风，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">人比黄花瘦。</strong></p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>词里的<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“黄花”</strong>可不是“黄花菜”，而是指得黄色的菊花。当时正值重阳节，李清照的丈夫并不在她的身边，每逢佳节倍思亲，他极度思念自己的丈夫，所以写下这首词。最后一句<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“人比黄花瘦”</strong>把可谓<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">点睛之笔</strong>，和同时代的著名词人刘永的那句<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”</strong>有异曲同工之妙。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-df9a5e68669efbc6.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-df9a5e68669efbc6.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">李清照</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">李清照是幸运的</strong>，作为一个女性，开明的父母从小培养读书识字，长大后又嫁给一个同样开明且爱他的赵明诚，可以继续着自己喜爱的文学创作；<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">但同时她又是不幸的</strong>，随着北宋灭亡，她被迫流亡南方，丈夫过早病逝，晚景颇凄凉。这首《阴花醉》隐隐地预示着他和丈夫之间注定要过早地阴阳相隔，自比菊花也是非常贴切，可谓<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">词如其人</strong>。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-84d7cf632c0bf5fd.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-84d7cf632c0bf5fd.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊花泡酒</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">《醉花阴》中的“东篱把酒黄昏后”又是重阳节的另外一个习俗，那就是和菊花泡制的酒，因为九九重阳节象征长寿，所以菊花酒也成为<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“长寿酒”</strong>。常饮菊花酒能延年益寿并非没有依据，因为菊花本身就是一味中药，就像<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">牡丹，芍药</strong>其实都是使用非常广泛的中药，只不过它们入药部位不一样，牡丹是以整株牡丹花<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">根的皮</strong>入药，所以也称为丹皮，芍药分白芍和赤芍，都是以<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">根</strong>入药，而菊花则是直接以<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">花</strong>入药。《神农本草经》上说菊花：</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">味苦，甘，性平。</strong></p></blockquote><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-8183702fe15a586d.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-8183702fe15a586d.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊花功效多</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">具有<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">清热解毒，平抑肝阳，散风明目</strong>等功效。中医认为大部分的高血压都是因为肝阳上亢引起的，菊花正好对症，降压药中有一种<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">“珍菊片”</strong>，主要成分就是野菊花粉和珍珠粉，副作用较纯西药降压片要小，安全性更高，而且价格较西药<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">便宜很多</strong>。现在很多西药降压片特别是外资药企生产的，大部分都要几块钱一粒，而珍菊片几块钱可以买一瓶了，一瓶60粒。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>中药的<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">性价比</strong>一向是很高的，现在宣传的那些价格贵的都是那些华而不实补药，比如冬虫夏草、鹿茸、 鱼翅等等。其实真正治病的中药价格都很便宜.比如《伤寒论》论里面一共<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">113</strong>个经典药方，基本上可以包治百病了，而这些药方当中最补的药除了<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">人参</strong>以外，就是<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">饴糖（麦芽糖）和红枣</strong>了。而人参也只是在病人极度虚弱的时候才用一下，而且还要辩证，不能乱用。平时更是不能随便服用，否则<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">反受其害</strong>。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-e3f6da53273b7ace.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-e3f6da53273b7ace.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">袁大头</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">袁世凯</strong>就是因为进补过头而在57岁就一命呜呼的。他从二十五六岁就开始进食补品，每天必吃一碗<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">鹿茸</strong>和一杯<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">人参</strong>茶，还经常吃<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">海狗肾、活络丹</strong>等补品，另外还养了两个奶妈供<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">人奶</strong>给他喝，所以虽然他平时看起来身材魁梧，其实雄壮，其实是用补品在透支自己的身体，越补身体越差，本来可以活80岁的身体，57岁就消耗殆尽了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实最好的补品就是<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">清补</strong>，把自己的身体内部清理干净，浑身舒畅，身体自然健康无病。中医治病有八种主要疗法：<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">汗、吐、下、和、温、清、消、补</strong>，补是排在最后一位的，而且，前面七种方法基本都是<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">在做减法，而不是加法<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></strong>。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-36cb56acafe101ca.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3285551-36cb56acafe101ca.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">菊花茶</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">所以，鱼翅燕窝人参鹿茸还是少吃为妙，平时不妨常喝菊花茶，清热解毒，延年益寿。想味道清淡一点可以选择<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">杭白菊</strong>，想醇厚一点可以选择<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box;\">昆仑雪菊</strong>。还可以根据自己的喜好加入枸杞，陈皮，冰糖等配料，总之定有一款适合您。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">不过菊花茶好喝，菊瓣壶精美，但是最好还是不要用菊瓣壶来泡菊花茶，容易窜味。我们还是应该选择透明的玻璃壶来泡菊花茶，这样可以一边饮菊花茶，一边赏壶内菊花，一举两得。</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('23', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3375123-11fedaebdcac06bc.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">图片来自网络</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>﻿﻿去年，朋友圈就行一句话：你现在的气质里，藏着你走过的路、读过的书和爱过的人，出自迈克尔-柯蒂斯导演的电影《卡萨布兰卡》﻿。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>于我们文字爱好者而言，我很想说：你的文章里，藏着你读过的书。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>前几天，有位简友看到我连续几遍文章被推首，便私信于我，想交流写作之事。他说，自己非常热爱文字，偶尔也在简书畅谈感想，但他困惑自己写不出好文章，半年多20多篇，6万多字，没有一篇被首页和主要专题收录，粉丝和点赞寥寥无几。他甚至怀疑自己智商低、没天赋。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>能看得出，他非常郁闷，也很焦灼。这种心情，我特别理解和同情，或多或少也经历过。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>也许出于习惯，我弱弱地问他，你平时喜欢读书吗？他说，每天业务那么忙，事务那么多，哪有时间看书！他还说，自来就没有读书的兴趣和习惯，一年也难得认真读上一本书。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“哥啊，你不爱读书还玩什么文字？”我话到嘴边，又噎了回去。毕竟我们素不相识，又何必出言不逊。最后，彼此寒暄几句便结束了对话。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>不用多说，大家也知道他的问题出在哪。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实，类似这位简友的人不在少数。就我的身边而言，总有一些同事不爱读书，为了出名挂号，却愿意去咬文嚼字，习惯凭着感觉堆砌成文，更有甚者寄希望粘贴复制东拼西凑，试想诸如此类的文章，就算颜值再高，遣词再好，架构再妙，也不可能有生命力，更不会入人法眼。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>很多时候，我们总喜欢羡慕别人的笔墨酣畅、文采飞扬，却不知隐藏在美文光鲜的背后，人家读过多少书，受过多少苦，少睡多少觉……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>杜甫有言，读书破万卷，下笔如有神。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>自古以来，但凡文学泰斗、文人墨客，哪个不是饱读诗书，谁又不是苦读圣贤。如果司马迁不潜心研读诗、书、礼、乐，就写不出《史记》这样的壮丽诗篇。如果不是古代圣人苦于研学考究，就不会有四书五经、唐诗宋词等中华瑰宝。这样的例子无法言尽，也不必赘述。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所以，写文章，不靠天赋，也不靠灵感，更不靠智商，靠的是腹有诗书，靠的是胸藏智慧。简而言之，就是看你读过多少书。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一篇好文章，表面上看是简单的文字叠加，实际上却是思想火花的闪放。如果不勤于读书，思想就会停止，又何来的火花呢！<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>与文字打交道的你我，或许都曾有这样的感受：有时侯任由你苦思冥想，也找不到半点思路，写不出只言片语。而这个时候，你停笔读读相关书籍，往往就会茅塞顿开，落笔时也就信手拈来。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>记得有一次我临危受命，被要求3天内出一篇研讨文章，且是自己从未触及的领域，当时完全懵逼。先是请教度娘，没有有价值线索。不得已只能泡在图书馆，查阅资料用了两天半，而下笔到成稿，还不足8个小时，几乎一气呵成。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那一次经历，给我的触动刻骨铭心，也让我真正意识到读书之于写作的价值所在。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>俗话说：“书犹药也，善读之可以医愚。”读书就是武装思想，充盈思路。如果不读书，不光你的大脑没有营养，你的灵魂也会逐渐蜕变。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所以我想说，你不读书，还想写出好文章，门都没有！于那位简友，于我，也于大家。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>最后，我想与大家共勉三毛的一句话。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>读书多了，容颜自然改变，许多时候，自己可能以为许多看过的书籍都成了过眼云烟，不复记忆，其实他们仍是潜在的，在气质里，在谈吐上，在胸襟的无涯，当然也可能显露在生活和文字里。</strong></blockquote><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\">');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('24', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-76341d33337b93de.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-76341d33337b93de.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"340\" data-width=\"600\" data-image-slug=\"76341d33337b93de\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">后来啊，我们也长大了</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>1<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">你知道那种怎么努力也没用的难过吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">你体会过自卑到极致的感觉吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">你有过全世界都不会喜欢你的怀疑吗？</p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>16岁那年读高一，成绩不好，不爱说话，性格内向，最喜欢做的事，就是一个人安安静静地坐在角落里看小说。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>同班同学相处了一整年，也认不全班上的人，化学老师甚至叫不出我的名字，看吧，那时候的自己，仿佛没有用处的微小尘埃，在光影交错里没有任何意义。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那时候成绩不好，却也活的开心，十几岁的小姑娘，活在自己的世界里也自得自乐。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>只是呢，人总是会改变的。尽管有时候懂得一些道理的代价未免太过残忍。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>虽然成绩不好，可是我作文写的还不错，经常被当作范文登上校报。当时全省的作文比赛只有我和我们班每次考试都是第一名女孩子入选了，可是一所学校只能派一名去参赛。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>结果我们班主任把我叫到办公室，第一次破天荒的问了我的成绩，就在我感动的无以复加的时候，她说，如果第一名在省里的比赛获奖了，一定能获得保送机会，而我就算获奖了，也没有特别的意义。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>对，猜的没错，我们班主任让我自动退出，把机会让给第一名。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当初还不明白优胜劣汰这种等级制度在人类世界才是运用到极致。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>只是很难过，原来唯一的一次被注意也只是做别人的背景。或许自己不优秀，就只能做别人的背景吧。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>应该算是顿悟，突然之间想通了，我不能一直做背景啊。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当时数学不好，便自己买回来了市面上所有的数学卷子，把高中的几本数学书全部找出来，把每一个知识点都标记下来，每做一道题，就把它划分到对应的知识点里。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实，学习应该算是最简单的事，因为答案永远都是客观的，你做对了便就是对了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>最后差不多做题做到吐的节奏，却终于找到了窍门，做的多了，就熟能生巧。看到一道题，瞬间就能找到做题思路。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>只要你努力一次，尝到努力之后有回报的感受，你就会相信，这世上没什么是你做不到的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>高三时，每次年级大考，我都能考进年级前二十，是吧，所有人都大跌眼镜，却又不得不承认，我确实不一样了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>只是你得到的每一样礼物，都是明码标价的，那以后我就再也不敢看自己喜欢的各种小说了，因为怕自己沉迷下去。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>因为习惯了做奥特曼，便不能露出受伤的样子，因为优秀变成了自己的标签，便再也不敢恣意妄为了。人就是这样复杂的动物，没人注意你时，你可以随心所欲，自甘堕落，看闲书，睡大觉，可一旦你变成聚光灯闪烁的那个点时，你就要活成别人期待的样子。</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-12830df0286b77b2.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-12830df0286b77b2.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"333\" data-width=\"600\" data-image-slug=\"12830df0286b77b2\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">唯独感情不能强求</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>2</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>20岁那年夏天的午后，去做家教的路上，我把手机弄丢了，迷路了半个小时后，同校的学长坚持要冒着39度高温送我过去。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>到现在我都清晰地记得那天的一切，阳光明晃晃地照过来，路边的妹子都打着彩虹太阳伞，街对面的小胖子手里拿着根可爱多边吃边笑，学长在我前面带路，他穿浅蓝色衬衫，我走在斜后方，看到他的侧脸冒着细微的汗珠。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>电影《大鱼》里说，<strong>如果你遇到自己喜欢的人时，时间就会在那一刻静止。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>可是那天过的太快了，快到我自己都没意识到，原来我已经有点喜欢学长了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>不过那之前的我，特别好吃，一天要吃五顿饭，早餐，午餐，晚餐，下午茶，外加夜宵。当时我认定自己一辈子就是为了吃才活着的，室友都叫我大胃王，我记得自己最夸张的时候，一星期吃了六顿小龙虾。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>外加我特别爱吃零食，嘴没有一刻是闲着的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>如此饭量，你们可以想象下我的体重。140斤配上168的身高，<strong>班上同学打趣我的时候说，我走路的时候，就像一个行走的巨人，这个比喻很形象。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>小胖子尚且还能说得上可爱，但我却是只大胖子。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一眼望过去就是个女巨人，丝毫谈不上可爱。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>遇见学长之前，我从来不觉得长得胖是件不好的事，因为那时候的我，不需要取悦任何人，只需要让自己开心就好了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>遇见学长之后，就是我漫长而艰辛的减肥史。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>每天早上五点半起床，天还是蒙蒙亮，操场上一个人都没有，我就开始扑哧扑哧地小跑了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>忍痛不买零食，不下馆子，顿顿去食堂，餐盘里只有绿色的蔬菜，吃之前还特意用白开水涮一遍，把油都涮掉。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那时候馋啊，有时候做梦都会梦到自己在吃小龙虾。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>买衣服的时候全部都买了S号，我对自己说，就当破釜沉舟了，现在想起来，真是敬佩那时候自己的勇气，如果减肥失败，难道裸体去上课？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大概是老天爷也被我感动到了，三个月瘦了四十斤。我看着自己以前的衣服，都觉得很神奇，原来曾经穿那么大的衣服。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>后来我要到学长的电话，也费尽心思制造了再相遇的机会。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>可是我们第二次见面时，他并没有认出我。他主动搭讪我，笑盈盈地和我聊天，那一瞬间我突然就不喜欢他了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>他不知道我因为喜欢他付出了多少，在他眼里我和其他漂亮女生没有差别，也仅仅只是人群里普通的那一个罢了，他甚至不曾记得我的样子。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>以前啊，有读者和我说，<strong>因为她唱歌的样子好看，我搭上半辈子的青春，我们的性格并不合适，每天都生活在对彼此的厌恶中。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不知道，我对学长的喜欢，是不是因为第一次见面的那个夏天，他穿浅蓝色衬衫特别好看，或者是因为他站出来帮了我。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我并没有和学长在一起，不过我已经从大胖子变成了大瘦子，前天秤体重的时候，只有98斤了。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-f6310d77e9950c17.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-f6310d77e9950c17.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"396\" data-width=\"720\" data-image-slug=\"f6310d77e9950c17\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">你不是一个人</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>3</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>大学毕业打算去上海闯一闯，认识的人都不看好我。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>各种各样的理由，仿佛我为自己的人生做决定，是不可理喻的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你一个人，那边又没有认识的人，多危险。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>魔都生活压力大，不适合你。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一个女孩子，安分守己找份工作，然后结婚生子就好了，瞎折腾什么？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>后来独自一人来到异乡，困难当然也是遇到很多，孤独的日子都数不清了，只是有天逛知乎的时候，看到一条回答，“有时候我们要走太多弯路”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这些年一步一步走过来，终于习惯了遇到问题，碰到麻烦都自己想办法解决，突然想到当初的那个被人抢了作文比赛名额，哭哭啼啼跑回家找爸妈的时候。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>原来不知不觉就长大了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>人生有无数种可能，希望你能变成自己喜欢的样子。</strong></p><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; box-sizing: border-box;\">愿你执迷不悟时，少受点伤，愿你幡然醒悟时，物是人是<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p></blockquote><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>安安决定日更了，欢迎交流讨论。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>关于转载问题：请统一简信联系我的经纪人<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.jianshu.com/users/98720347038f\" target=\"_blank\">阿肆呢</a></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>旧书《感谢你来过我的世界》冷买中，感谢支持。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-3674101421a936a1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/569985-3674101421a936a1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"1280\" data-width=\"960\" data-image-slug=\"3674101421a936a1\"></p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('25', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-2e3bb6733772ead4.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2016年4月，在桂林。</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>文/点苍</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我是一个闲不住、喜欢东奔西走的人。三毛的“天涯”一直被我想往。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在结婚以前，趁着单身，独自去过很多地方，看过许多风景，经历过许多人和事。婚后，脚步仍旧没有停下来，因为遇到一个喜欢旅行的伴侣。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>新婚时，我们做了婚后第一次旅行，在香港呆足了港澳通行证所能允许逗留的七天，仍旧意尤未尽。对于香港这座城市，我始终有一种难解的情缘，无论去多少次，每一次都宛如初到宝地，总是满怀新鲜和喜悦之情。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>第二次两个人旅行，女儿风宝已经一岁零五个月，由于去的是滇西北的高海拔地区，九月下旬的天气已渐至寒冷，所以最终没有带她去，把她放在了奶奶家。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那一趟旅行，第一站去了丽江。虽然两个人此前都分别去过，但婚后两个人去丽江还是头一次。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>第一晚住在丽江古城狮子山上一间观景客栈。睡到半夜，我一伸手没有摸到孩子，突然一阵惊悸，嗖地从床上坐起来，大喊着“娃娃哪去了？娃娃不见了”，然后开了灯跳下床往床底下看，以为孩子滚到了床底下。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这时，老公从梦中惊醒，懵懂地望着我说，我们根本没带风宝出来，你是不习惯她不在你身边吧？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我方才如梦初醒，想起这趟旅行根本没有带孩子出来。发生这样的事，完全是因为那个小丫头从呱呱坠地就从来没有离开过我。每一个夜晚，她都躺在我的身旁，像春天的小嫩芽一样在寂静的夜里静悄悄地生长。而每一天夜里，我时不时地摸一摸她身上的被子、看她有没有踢被子早已经成为一种习惯，所以，旅行中夜宿客栈，才会发生这种让人啼笑皆非的事情。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那之后，我决定从此以后外出旅行，无论去哪里，去多远的地方，都要带上她。当旅行结束，回到家时，看见她眼泪汪汪地看着我们时，更加让我后悔这一趟旅行没有带上她。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>到了第二年的九月，风宝两岁零五个月，我们带上她，开启了三人行的旅行模式。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>为了迎合小朋友的喜好，从第一次带她旅行开始，去的大部分是有海的地方。</p>﻿<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-7a4698cffd9bd3ef.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2013年9月，在三亚</p></p><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>第一次去了三亚。那时风宝还是个只能半句半句地说话、走路会摇晃的幼童。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝第一次坐飞机，不愿意独自坐自己的位子，我只好和空乘人员沟通后，抱着她。可是飞行途中，她竟然大喊大叫起来。<strong>她说，请开飞机的叔叔停一停，我不坐了，我要下去。</strong>引得众人哈哈大笑，她却还是固执地要求飞行员停下来让她下机。后来好不容易才安抚下来。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>到了三亚，住进海棠湾一家五星酒店。那次旅行，我们充当了一回成功人士，订了睡一夜半个月薪水便不翼而飞的豪华酒店，只因为这样的酒店里有干净的私家海滩和小朋友也能玩耍的温泉游戏池，还有设施齐全的儿童游乐园。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>每天全家睡到自然醒，去酒店餐厅吃丰盛的早餐，然后抹上防晒霜、趿着拖鞋去海滩。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>九月的三亚，虽然几乎每日都有降雨，但天气还是闷热。每天带风宝在海滩上玩沙，在游泳池里戏水，在酒店的躺椅上晒太阳。从早到晚所见的一草一木，路过的一只蜗牛都令小朋友感到兴奋。遇见酒店的工作人员和我们打招呼的时候，她会礼貌的回应。如果对方很年轻，她就会多加几句赞美的话，比如你真漂亮，你真帅，所以在酒店里，她一个非常受欢迎的小客人。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那次旅行，也是风宝出生以来，第一次看见海。尽管天气晴朗，海面上风平浪静，不时扑上来拍打沙滩的海浪也极其温柔，可是当她看见我站在不远的沙滩上，海浪向我拍打过来，淹没我的脚踝时，她却吓得哇哇大哭。等到我回到她身边，她再也不让我走到海浪打得到的地方去。<strong>她说，害怕大海把妈妈带走。﻿</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-eb791d53df3d0f4e.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2016年4月，在涠洲岛</p></p><br style=\'color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>很多人认为，太小的孩子因为没有记忆，所以没必要带他们出钱旅行，既花钱又花精力，简直是出钱找罪受。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我并不认同这样的说法。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>因为我就是一个小小年纪就跟随父亲东奔西走的人。由于父亲年纪轻轻就做了国营工厂的副厂长，所以一年中大半部分时间都在外出差。当我有风宝这么大的时候，已经跟随父亲出差许多次，辗转于各个城市之间，直到上小学，这种充当父亲小旅伴的生活才算是告一段落。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>尽管那时我还小，像很多人说的还不大能记事，可是去过的城市，到过的地方，甚至发生过的一些事情至今都深刻在我的脑海。也正是因为小小年纪就跟随父亲去过许多大城市，逛过许多名胜，到过许多风景如画的地方，也进过许多守备森严的职能部门和单位，所以才会有对外面世界的向往，才会一心想要行走天涯，探知未曾到达过的地域。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>也正因为幼年跟随父亲走南闯北，长大之后，虽然我只是外表看上去瘦小柔弱的姑娘，却有独自去看世界的气魄，敢去追求自己想要的生活，尝试独自在完全陌生的城市工作和生活。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所以，<strong>我相信，一个人若童年时看过精彩的世界，长大之后，绝不会是一只坐井观天、目光短浅的井底之蛙。</strong></p>﻿<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-74fc2ab98e446a69.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2016年4月，在涠洲岛</p></p><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>从风宝两岁半开启了一家三口的三人之旅后，每一年春暖花的时节，利用老公的公休假，我们都会做一次十天半个月的长途旅行，多半是去有海的地方。有时，一年内也会出门很多次，或远或近，去很多个地方。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝刚好三岁的时候，我们在厦门呆了半个月，每天在鼓浪屿闲逛，或是在海滩上玩沙子拣贝壳，玩累了，找一家甜品店吃甜口，或是一家海鲜店吃海鲜。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝满四岁的时候，我们去了成都，不但尝遍成都美食，也带孩子去了她向往的熊猫基地、喜欢的海洋馆和动物园。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝四岁五个月，我们带上风宝和外公外婆，从昆明开车去重庆做自驾游。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝五岁五个月的时候，我们去了涠洲岛。租一张能载三个人的电动车，每天吃过早饭，一家三口骑电动车沿着环岛路行驰，看到有海滩就停下来玩水拣贝壳捞小鱼，看见有卖香蕉木瓜的停下来买一堆，看见风景如画的地方就停下来拍几张照，傍晚的时候去海鲜市场买刚刚打捞出上来的海鲜，极其悠闲自在。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>无论去哪里，我们不跟团，不赶景点，除了在有宜家的城市会逛逛宜家，几乎不逛商业中心、不购物。我们总是提前做好出行计划，出门前便订好所到各地的酒店、机票、高铁票、门票。因为风宝还小，所以不会太早起来赶时间赶景点，总是等她睡够，然后吃饱，我们才慢条拾理的出门，她说想去哪里，我们就去哪里。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>虽然在不跟旅行团的前提下，带小朋友外出旅行是件很辛苦的事，不但要携带大箱的行李奔波往返，还要注意孩子的安全，甚至饮食卫生，以防孩子走失或是吃坏肚子生病。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>每次出门总要为孩子带上足够多的换洗衣服，衣服鞋子都必须适合旅行。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>要带上各种各样的儿童常备药。许多父母带孩子出门，总是以为现在满大街都是药店，怕麻烦就不带药，却忽略凡事总有意外。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>记得去年带风宝去北海涠洲岛，在昆明至南宁的火车上，同在一个软卧包厢的一个小男孩突发高烧，带着一男一女两个小童出门的老人急得手足无措，列车上的医务室又没有儿童专用的药物，所幸我出门总是带着一个大药包，赶紧打开箱子给孩子拿了退烧药。半小时之后，孩子的高烧终于退了，两位老人家千恩万谢。所以，<strong>若带小孩出远门，孩子的常用药一定要随身携带，毕竟，一旦孩子生病，不是随时随地都能买到应急的药品。</strong>这也算是这些年来带风宝频繁出游而积累的一点旅行经验。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在最近三四年的时间里，我们带着风宝去了三亚、厦门、福州、成都、重庆、宜宾、北海涠洲岛、桂林、阳溯，至于云南省境内也游了个遍。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>而三百公里外的大理，一年里总要去个好几次，有时是一家三口，有时是我单独带上她，有时会呆上一个星期，有时可能只是一个周末的时间。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>朋友们都说，从来没有见过那么喜欢大理的一家人，简直把大理当作了后花园，有事没事就开车过去。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>确实如此，大理是我们的后花园。每一次去大理，我们一家三口总喜欢在古城里闲逛，走累了就找一家咖啡厅或是西餐厅坐下来喝咖啡吃甜店，或是爬到城墙上看苍山顶上的云和头顶蔚蓝明净的天空。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>或者，我们开车去环洱海。一整天沿着环海路行走，走走停停。在有水的地方戏水，在有湿地的地方挂起吊床，晒着午后的太阳打个盹，一天就这样在闲暇舒适里度过。老公说，这才是游大理最正确的打开方式。</p>﻿<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-200ea62496958c4f.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2014年4月，在厦门鼓浪屿</p></p><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>眼看又是春暖花开，风宝像冬眠之后醒来的小熊宝宝，她的小小的好奇心在渐至温暖的天气里又开始激动起来，因为，马上又要出门旅行了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>虽然有时候，老公逗她说，带你出门实在太麻烦、太伤脑筋，不如你别去了，去奶奶或者外婆家，我和妈妈单独出去旅行好不好？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>风宝听到这样的话，必定会伤心得眼睛红红，眼看泪水就要掉下来。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这时，我总是对她说，爸爸只是逗你的，我们出门怎么可能不带上你呢？要知道，<strong>没有你的旅行，去哪里都不快乐呀！</strong>她听了，破泣为笑。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>昨天上街，风宝看见路边一张广告上的蒙娜丽莎画像。她问我，这是谁？我说，蒙娜丽莎，这是一幅非常有名的油画，真品收藏在法国巴黎的卢浮宫，等你长大了，自己去看。她说，你陪我去吧！我说，那是更远的地方，长大了自己去吧！现在爸爸妈妈只是陪你走我们所能陪你走的路。她说，好！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>亲爱的孩子，我们总是尽自己的能力带你去旅行，陪你一起看精彩世界的一部分，至于剩下的路和未来的世界，就全靠你自己了！</strong></p>﻿﻿<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1243121-c7c8104f469d0357.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1600/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">2016年，本地</p></p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('26', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/4748481-062696f17d9e2307.JPG?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1080/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">图片发自简书App</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>犹记得刚上大学时，军训后第一次拍照。我咧开灿烂而坚定的笑容，心里默想着五年后我一定要成为学校的骄傲。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>时光荏苒，毕业季转眼到来。在仓促的考试、答辩、聚会之后，终于不舍的和大学说再见。拿到毕业照的那天，我的心是沉的，照片上的自己被同学遮了半边脸，一个勉强而故意的笑容害羞的藏到了后面。其实只有自己知道，我没有成为学校的骄傲，反而是听没出息的学子。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>五年大学时光，我除了按部就班的上课，例行公事的参加些活动，偶尔考个无关痛痒的证书，像样的跑几天步，泡几天图书馆。大部分时间都在无边无际的异想天开。想着毕业时一定要收获知识与能力，想着一定要成为理想中优秀的自己，想着……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我却从来没有真正坚持下来，做成一件引以为豪的事情。三天打鱼两天晒网，永远不可能实现目标。我就像那只寒号鸟，当冬天来临，就是我的死期。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>一晃工作半年多了，我依然在踏入社会的那一刻，重新开导自己，来日方长机会还有我还年轻。下一个五年一定活成最好的自己，奋斗出新的高度。是的，我又陷入了安慰的怪圈儿和借口的陷阱。不知不觉我再次成为了时间的奴隶。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在风平浪静的岁月里，要么计划着明天开始会更好，要么数数日子先图享乐。每当听说熟悉的某某，做出了新成绩，做到了自己想做的事情，就赌气似的暗示自己，立即行动一定要超过他。若是原来不如自己的人，或者平时看似庸碌、不显山不露水的同学突然更新了人生的状态，向着成功之路越走越近。自己就忍不住掩面叹息和悔恨，咬牙要振作起来扭转乾坤。渐渐的，被自己时不时的\"雄心壮志\"骗了无数次，以为自己一直在挣扎奋斗，可实际上都是在自欺欺人。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>原定了九十天专心学习，不再看电视剧的计划。如今才到第十五天，电视瘾又开始蠢蠢欲动。原来想好每天早起吃饭再上班的打算，才坚持了四五天。原以为在简书上日更，会是一件易如反掌的事，如今才一个星期就开始了中断。诸如此类，似乎二十五年以来从没有坚持到底过。这样的人生到头来，也不过一辈子的如果可以从来的悔字。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实，我有那么多的理由可以说服自己。年迈的父母需要赡养，自己的理想需要追寻，生活的真谛需要探索，诚挚的心灵需要发现……而那一切的一切都需要管住自己。一个没有自律性的人，怎配体验幸福的人生？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不会再上自己的当了！我不会再相信光凭想象就可以收获宝藏，不下狠心就能改掉坏毛病，不去行动就能证明自己的决心。那都是痴人说梦。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>就让骗人的自己死去吧，我将勇敢面对一个真实的自我，一个跌倒过太多次、虚伪过太多次、说无数次大话的自己。一个需要外界帮助，需要重新定位的自己。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我相信只有从内心深处，接受了失败的现实，才能开始走向成功。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>此时此刻，很庆幸我真正看清了一部分自己，我是不可能一鸣惊人的，我需要学习士兵突击里的许三多，脚踏实地去做一些有意义的事，有助于修正自己的事。别再相信那个口是心非、甜言蜜语的自己了，正视缺点是一种更大的进步。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>愿如我一样曾经欺骗自己的人，别再相信自己了，认清事实正视自己才能迎来胜利的曙光！</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('27', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2593216-ad4953bf4475fe63.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1080/q/50\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p class=\"image-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; min-height: 22px; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;\">图片发自简书App</p></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>犹记得17和18岁的时光，我看《桃花扇》，由于文言文的理解难度，就下定决心自己翻译，每天吃饭后在家人出去散步直到回来期间做这件事，这段时间里我趴在窗户口，因家境不好家里人不到全黑是不开灯的，就着天际映照来的那抹夕阳，我总是坚涩的在爬字，这都源于自己文学底子不够，因此三分之一的内容需要逐字逐句的查字典，那段岁月真真是痛苦和快乐的结合体，煎熬和喜悦渗透在一起，却未料到多年后的今天会再回忆起，更未想到那滋味会成为贪婪的回顾，会成为深刻的渴望，渴望回到那段时空，接着会有一会儿思绪的失控……﻿<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>后来看冯友兰的《中国哲学史》，似乎又回到了同样的时光，又开始重温痛苦、快乐、煎熬、喜悦，且那感受比那时更强烈，因着那时的娱乐与现今比可视为无物，那时啃书带来的损失仅是没与家人散步。而今，每个读书的时光里总会有刷屏、玩微、中国好声音，爸爸去哪儿了，非诚勿扰，K歌……，当简单和艰难相遇，当放纵和约束相遇，当书写与视频相遇，当学术和娱乐相遇，很多人选择的往往是简单、放纵、视频、娱乐，这无可厚非却并不见得是对的。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>看古文于我是件累事，有时看着一句话只能像是拍照一样看到字面，无法参透其意，纠结着那些简明扼要的字或是词，总是得借问度娘，然后在书上密密麻麻的标注着。多年来由于对书的热爱和看书的习惯，我已然对品各式的书都产生了浓浓的欲望，因此我的选择坚定而轻松，因为这是我幸福的源泉之一。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但观当今社会人群，集体放纵和集体屏蔽文化现象严重，捧书之人少之又少，这是我每每看书之余都会焦虑的地方，现如今因着女儿对传统文学的漠视和排斥更让我的焦虑加深，从心理学角度而言同样的痛苦在别人身上和在自己至爱之人身上的感受是截然不同的，现在我深刻理解了，我不知如何与我女儿解说《论语》的伟大，因为我也是成人后主动去学才理解的，我无法告知文学与闲情小说是二个概念，因为我也是与书打多年交道后方悟，我无法让她理解“慎独”，因为拼音组词里它们是分离的，我无法做到的还有很多很多……﻿</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>&nbsp; &nbsp;每天的二小时“咖啡+文学”（以后如果开咖啡馆能成功，我就取这个名字）的时光把心里空荡的位置都填满了，像是孤独的人被爱人拥抱，像是幸福触手可及了……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这样的幸福于我而言是，别人却不见得认同，常常有人从身边走过嘟囔着这小姑娘是要考什么这么认真？没人觉得我是纯粹看书，想想世上已很少有纯粹的事情可做了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>翻看读书笔记，《中国哲学史》是我2014年看的，距今已2年多，后来还看了钱穆老先生的几本书也是如此艰难，那时的自己一副天将降大任于斯人也的境界，总想着把感受分享大家，去影响别人，对着女儿说教，而今看来觉得自己不免矫情，有所追求固然不错，可是要求却只能对自己，当然BOSS要求职员可以，谁发工资谁说了算！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实看书也好，写作也好，刷屏也好，玩微也好，这不是个人自己的选择吗？没有伤害任何人，只要清醒认识到这是自己选择的人生，未来的每一步都和现在的每一步息息相关，结果也要承受的起，很多人都说年轻时输得起，我不赞同，我个人觉得年轻所以输不起，别人都在努力奋斗，而你却在随波逐流，还美名自己做喜欢的事就好。女儿的人生也是一样，我只说你的人生，选择得你自己来，但是后果也自己担，我只负责解答你想问的，仅供参考。这一说，女儿倒是慎重起来了。</p><blockquote style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 20px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); border-left-width: 6px; border-left-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>已成之思想，若继续能应环境之需要，人亦自然继续持之；﻿即时有新见，亦自然以之比附于旧系统之上；﻿<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">盖旧瓶未破，有新酒自当以旧瓶装之。﻿必至环境大变，旧思想不足以应时势之需要；﻿应时势而起之新思想既极多极新，旧瓶不能容，于是旧瓶破而新瓶代兴。﻿<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;——摘自冯友兰《中国哲学史》下</blockquote>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('28', '\n				\n	<p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2542851-993063cc69b29bdd.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>01</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在我的生命当中，有一个，永远无私爱我的女人。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但我小时候，却经常“讨厌”她。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我讨厌她雨天递过来的红伞，“这是女孩子用的伞，我不要！”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我讨厌她炒菜时加的青椒，“青椒的味，我不喜欢，今天的饭，我不吃了！”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我讨厌天微微冷时她强制我加的衣服：“我不怕冷！穿这个衣服不好看！”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我还讨厌她的唠叨，无论是当面还是电话里：“我都这么大了，知道过马路小心，知道天冷了要穿衣，知道下雨要拿伞……你不用管我！”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>到今年，我已经认识她25年了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>在我面前，她的心，一直是一片裸露的空地，可以让我随意践踏。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>也许她会哭，但我并不知道。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>别人说：“爱人会在你面前哭，而母亲，只会在你背后，悄悄哭。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>02<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>是的，她前些天在电话里哭了，因为，我家进了盗贼，丢了很多东西。这其中，也包括我自己攒钱买的单反相机。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>其实我对财物并不看重，当然，也可能是丢东西丢惯了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我说：“妈，丢了就丢了吧，都是身外之物，以后都可以用钱买回来。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>但没说两句，她在电话那头就哽咽了：“都是我把东西弄丢的……”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>从中午到晚上，我每隔一小时给我妈打一个电话：“妈，没事的，破财免灾哈……”然后再和我爸说几句：“爸，快安慰安慰我妈。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>记忆中的母亲一直是高大而坚强的，但现在，为什么我越发觉出她的柔软和弱小了？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不知道。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>难道仅仅是因为她变老了，而我长大了？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>03<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>萧红说：“女性的天空是低矮的。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不知道。我只知道我妈的天空，就是我们的家。她一辈子像一个陀螺，永远围着家转，被命运的鞭子催赶着，一圈，又一圈。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>过年回家时，我用仅剩的钱给我妈买了一个镯子，她像孩子一样高兴，开心完，便把镯子放回盒子里，准备放起来。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我立刻阻止：“妈，镯子就是用来带的，你放起来干什么。”然后不经过她同意，强行给她戴在了手上。我分明看到了她眼角的泪光，轻微闪烁。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>原来父母和子女，永远也不平等。当父母给我们买东西的时候，我们笑了；当我们给他们东西的时候，他们却哭了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我最初以为有了钱才可以孝敬父母，但现在看来，亲情，多少金钱也换不来。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>去年八月，我在家待了一个月，每天早上，和母亲出门散步。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“妈，我九月开学以后你就不要一个人走了，一个人，不安全。”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我妈同意了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>04<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>今年52，她这一辈子，对命运是驯服的，但不是软弱，因为其中，很大一部分是负责的精神。很多时候，她的坚韧，力量比反抗更为强大。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>她结婚前几年，因为迟迟没有生育，经常被我爷爷奶奶欺负。我爷爷以前是军人，脾气暴躁，做事没有分寸，很多次，还打了她。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>后来家里开小店，邻居老太太看我妈年轻，有意无意摆出长者姿态，为一些小事，和我妈争吵。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我爸不太管事，亲戚妯娌三姑六婆，各种人际往来全靠我妈应付。人家看我爸不是个管事的人，自然也看轻了我妈。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>那些年周围各种开矿，因为煤价贵，人们自发组织的捡炭队伍浩浩荡荡。我妈二话不说，也加入了其中。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>整整二十年，她的青丝里有了好多白发。其实她骨子里是个非常柔弱的人，但那些年，她和我爷爷斗，爷爷最后被斗地没了脾气；她和看不起我们的邻人吵架，一次又一次，邻人后来所有的东西，都在我家买；她应对各种亲戚往来，摆事实讲道理，眼里不揉一点沙子，很多人都很害怕她；她一个人晚上捡炭，日复一日，捡回一吨又一吨……</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我上大学那年，母亲病倒了，大病，差一点，就离开了我们。县医院、市医院、省人民医院，辗转三个月，最后才回到家中。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>中间我去医院看她，她躺着，脸很白，看到我，然后眼睛湿润了：“我把咱家的钱都花光了……把给你们攒的钱花完了……”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>为什么你的眼里常含泪水？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你一生节俭，为什么就不能花点钱？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>你是我们的天，天塌了，要钱还有个屁用！</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>05<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>去KTV时，我会点一首《母亲》，很老的歌，但我觉得很有味道。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“你入学的新书包有人给你拿，你雨中的花折伞有人给你打，你爱吃的那三鲜馅有人她给你包……”在大家快笑岔气时，我认真唱完了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>人总是在一瞬间长大，现在，我能真切地感受到自己的成长。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我开始心疼母亲眼里不经意流出的风霜，开始习惯并享受她的唠叨，也开始向她唠叨：“在家好好吃饭，天冷了穿好衣服，走路慢点……”</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我不愿让她变成孤单的背影，也不愿让她苍老成落寞的影子。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我已经长大，可以站出来了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>告诉她:</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>“你那么爱我，今后请让我来照顾你。”</p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>定期更新，欢迎交流讨论。</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>关于转载问题：请统一简信联系我的经纪人<a style=\"color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.jianshu.com/u/3d62e7b7cfa2\" target=\"_blank\">加油小毛虫</a>。</p>');
INSERT INTO `articlecontent` VALUES ('29', '\n				\n	<p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>你是一个懒癌患者吗？</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>你跟懒癌做过斗争吗？</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>你有没有感到克服懒癌症非常困难？</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>怎样有效的克服懒癌呢？</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-5b2079e57fb7ba94.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-5b2079e57fb7ba94.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"386\" data-width=\"580\" data-image-slug=\"5b2079e57fb7ba94\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>毒品为什么会让人上瘾？因为毒品改变了人类大脑的“快乐机制”。原本的“快乐机制”是用来奖励人的生存和繁殖行为的，比如吃饭、性活动等，它使我们的大脑产生舒服的感觉。这种“快乐机制”通过化学语言多巴胺来传递。但是，毒品对大脑中“快乐机制”的刺激远远比人类正常活动比如性活动的刺激、中奖的刺激等要快速、强烈得多。当人习惯于这种外界持续的强刺激给自己带来的快乐时，就很难再适应自己天然的“快乐机制”产生的兴奋感了。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当人无法通过自己的行动，带来感悟和体验的快感，就会喜欢享受当下的“新闻”、“新知”、“娱乐”、“游戏”给自己带来的这种即时的满足感。这个道理就好像许多人不是没有目标，而是给自己制定目标以后，“懒癌”发作最终导致目标没有达成。比如，你想考过英语六级、想考研、考博，这一定需要一个漫长的看书、学习和练习的过程才能通过考试。但往往你看一会书就会忍不住拿出手机刷一下朋友圈、聊几句微信。因为通过做这些简单无脑的事情，你能获得“即时的满足感”。而阅读、学习、提升自己这样的事情都是属于“延时的满足”，短时间内不会能让自己收获很大的满足感，所以你很容易去放弃，去拖延。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>人之所以都会有这种天生“短视”，喜欢即时的反馈和满足感，是因为人类生存和演化的天性造成的。几百万年前，我们的祖先还茹毛饮血的时候，资源稀缺，吃了上顿没下顿，于是大脑持续的分泌化学物质，它们促使人类去寻找并摄入食物，热量越高越好，自身的脂肪储存的越多越好。如果没有这种机制，人类很可能存活不到今天。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>可远离了原始以后，我们进化出了更高级的控制单元，我们学会了计划，学会了为达成长期目标放弃短期利益。但人类大脑中原始的那部分并没有消亡，它依然在时刻争夺着身体的控制权，促使我们孜孜不倦的寻求即时的满足感。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-5dbbd87548ced9b1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-5dbbd87548ced9b1.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"900\" data-width=\"1200\" data-image-slug=\"5dbbd87548ced9b1\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>想想婴儿刚出生最原始的生理反应，饿了就哭，不给吃的就一直哭，吃饱了就笑，这就是即时满足反应。同样的，如果一件事能短时间看到反馈（成果），就容易去做。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>为什么学习一个小时很难，而磕一个小时的瓜子很容易。因为每一个磕瓜子的动作都是有即时的回报的，每个磕瓜子动作都会得到相应的一粒瓜子吃，大脑的即时满足很快就来了，而学习了一个小时，得不到明显的成果和反馈。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所以，为什么你打开手机想要背单词，却鬼使神差的戳开了微博和微信；为什么你打开电脑想要听讲座，却不知不觉得看起了电影和电视剧；为什么你晚饭吃了不少，睡前却还是管不住自己伸向零食的手；这些的本质都是大脑的那个“原始部分”在作怪。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>那么，要如何克服呢？</strong></p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-74bd87d39fd3e3ee.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-74bd87d39fd3e3ee.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"314\" data-width=\"500\" data-image-slug=\"74bd87d39fd3e3ee\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>简单的说，<strong>就是想办法用“延时的满足感”来替代“即时的满足感”。</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>有人可能说，让我延时满足，是不是要一直延到死再满足？当然不是。延时满足绝不是压抑自己的需要，是适当的迟一些再满足。只是需要你和自己的大脑做一个约定。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>根据美国作家凯利•麦格尼格尔（Kelly McGonigal）教授的《自控力》（THE WILLPOWER INSTINCT）中提到的一个方法：等待10分钟。在诱惑面前安排10分钟的等待时间，如果你10分钟之后还想要，那你就可以拥有它，但是这期间，你应当要时刻想着长远的利益。我们可以把这条策略总结为：创造一点距离，让拒绝变得容易。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>比如两三岁的孩子，马上要吃苹果，你可以先不给他，不让他“即时满足”，让他等一会，安静一会，再给他；五六岁的孩子，到了商场看到玩具以后想要玩具，你可以先不给他，过一段时间再给他……通过对孩子的这种延时处理，帮助孩子提高等待满足的时间。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>比如在学习工作时，想拿出手机玩之前，可以告诉自己：“等10分钟之后再玩，如果10分钟以后还想玩，就可以玩。”但在这期间，人通常会思考玩手机对学习效率会产生什么样的影响。有了这样的思考，10分钟过后，一般也不会再想着拿起手机玩。这个方法还可以运用到那些“我要做”但又总拖延的事情上。对于这类事情，可以告诉自己：先坚持做10分钟，10分钟之后如果觉得不想做，就可以放弃。但通常只要不是自己厌恶的事情，开始做了以后很容易就忘了10分钟的约定，不知不觉的就会做很久。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>等待10分钟的方法是基于“即时奖励”的原理提出的。还有一种方法是基于“未来奖励”这个角度，从长远利益出发提出的策略，叫做：降低延迟折扣率。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>我们的大脑习惯于给未来的回报打折，但是每个人打的折扣是不一样的。有人打的折扣很高，因而未来的奖励对这类人来说估值会很低，所以他们比较容易选择屈从于眼前的诱惑；而有的人打的折扣会比较低，因而未来的奖励对这部分人来说估值会很高，他们通常更关注这个更大的奖励，并耐心等待它的到来。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>当你受到诱惑要做与长期利益相悖的事的时候，可以尝试：想象一下，你的这个行为意味着你为了即时的满足感而放弃了更好的长期奖励；想象你已经得到了长期的奖励，未来的你正在享受着自控的成果。问一问自己，愿意放弃它来换取正在诱惑你的短暂快感吗？这套方法就是为了增加“未来奖励”的价值，降低延迟折扣率。</p><p class=\"image-package\" style=\'width: 700px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 25px; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-left: -40px; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><img style=\"border: 0px currentColor; transition:0.25s ease-in-out; border-image: none; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-a1226790815f832e.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3372774-a1226790815f832e.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip\" data-height=\"366\" data-width=\"550\" data-image-slug=\"a1226790815f832e\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>比如你正在复习考研，不经意间想拿出手机玩，在玩之前，想象一下现在的时间玩了手机就是放弃了复习的时间，你很可能因此而考研失败，这是你想看的吗？想象未来你考上理想学校和专业的研究生，围绕在亲戚朋友的夸赞和羡慕中的情景。想象你凭借着研究生的学历进入世界500强或大型企业工作，而跟你同级的小明因为是本科学历连面试的机会都没有。你愿意放弃那个未来继续玩手机吗？</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>这个方法最重要的点就是你对未来的期待是怎样的？你对未来的期待越高越明晰，你的延迟折扣率就会越低，你就越愿意放弃眼前的利益而追求更长期的利益。所以，知道自己真正想要什么非常重要。只有你真正想要的东西才可能触发你内心的动机，为了它，你才有可能放弃即时奖励带来的满足感。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>所谓对未来的期待，其实就是“梦想”，当一个人有了“梦想”，他也就拥有更大的内心动力去坚持做那些能够帮助实现梦想的事情，放弃或避开那些可能阻碍梦想实现的诱惑。当一个人可以清晰地知道自己想要什么并能够时刻警醒自己，就可以很好的“以终为始”地做那些重要的事情。</p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'>END</p><p><hr style=\'border-width: 1px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; height: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-top-style: solid; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>若您觉得这篇文章不错，请点击“喜欢”；若想获取更多好文，请点击“关注”</strong></p><p style=\'margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: -apple-system, \"SF UI Text\", Arial, \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\'><strong>提供思想和方法，节省职场人的试错成本和学习时间</strong></p>');

